ngle order placed with a USD value higher than this amount will not execute. \n—  Decimal & Thousands Separator Formatting \n\nThe decimal and thousands separators shown in this article may differ from the formats displayed on our trading platforms. Review our article on how we use points and commas for more information.","datePublished":"2026-06-29T00:00:00.000Z","wordCount":172,"timeRequired":"PT1M"}]}</script><link data-rh="true" id="css-onload" type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="https://www.kraken.com/css/facade-onload/7857.css"/><link data-rh="true" rel="shortcut icon" sizes="32x32" href="https://assets-cms.kraken.com/files/51n36hrp/facade/3a7d4120afc2fbd62d39d9d063fcefc829e24874.ico"/><link data-rh="true" rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/28078745169c7bdfbe6985f51641da71c7ba83e0-180x180.png"/><link data-rh="true" rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/927f03956c6dc12aaa8dd1af8bb32fb927a6de89-33x32.svg"/><link data-rh="true" rel="alternate" href="https://support.kraken.com/articles/4844359082772-linear-multi-collateral-derivatives-contract-specifications" hrefLang="x-default"/><link data-rh="true" rel="alternate" href="https://support.kraken.com/articles/4844359082772-linear-multi-collateral-derivatives-contract-specifications" hrefLang="en-us"/><link data-rh="true" rel="alternate" href="https://support.kraken.com/es/articles/4844359082772-linear-multi-collateral-derivatives-contract-specifications" hrefLang="es-es"/><link data-rh="true" rel="alternate" href="https://support.kraken.com/es-la/articles/4844359082772-linear-multi-collateral-derivatives-contract-specifications" hrefLang="es-la"/><link data-rh="true" rel="alternate" href="https://support.kraken.com/de/articles/4844359082772-linear-multi-collateral-derivatives-contract-specifications" hrefLang="de-de"/><link data-rh="true" rel="alternate" href="https://support.kraken.com/fr/articles