  [&amp;_button[aria-controls^=&#x27;content-&#x27;]]:!relative"><div class="ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0"><div class="relative min-w-full"><button id="85bl7ei4pfcn0gwysz59" type="button" aria-controls="content-85bl7ei4pfcn0gwysz59" aria-expanded="false" class="bg-ds-accordion focus-visible:rounded-ds-2 focus:outline-ds-accordion outline-offset-ds-accordion w-full cursor-pointer border-0 py-0 text-start focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 disabled:cursor-not-allowed ps-0 hover:bg-ds-accordion-hover group"><div class="py-ds-5 flex w-full items-center shadow-ds-accordion"><div class="text-ds-body1 text-ds-accordion-primary group-hover:text-ds-accordion-hover" data-testid="title">Perpetual Contract Specifications</div><div class="ps-ds-7 ms-auto flex flex-shrink-0 items-center" data-testid="chevron-down"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0 w-ds-icon-md h-ds-icon-md" name="ChevronDownSmall"><path d="M7.5 9.98291L11.2045 13.6874C11.6438 14.1268 12.3562 14.1268 12.7955 13.6874L16.5 9.98291" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="fill-transparent stroke-ds-icon-dimmed"></path></svg></div></div></button><div id="content-85bl7ei4pfcn0gwysz59" aria-labelledby="85bl7ei4pfcn0gwysz59" data-testid="content-85bl7ei4pfcn0gwysz59" style="display:block" class="transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out overflow-hidden max-h-0 opacity-[0]"><div class="pb-4"><div class="space-y-6 pb-8 pt-2 [&amp;&gt;:not(:has(table))]:mx-auto [&amp;&gt;:not(:has(table))]:w-full [&amp;&gt;:not(:has(table))]:max-w-[var(--article-max-width)]"><div class="text-ds-primary text-ds-body1 ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0"><div class="[&amp;_a:hover]:font-inherit [&amp;_a:hover]:underline [&amp;_a]:no-underline [&amp;_blockquote]:ps-ds-6 [&amp;_blockquote]:text-ds-body1 [&amp;_blockquote]:before:bg-ds-dimmed [&amp;_blockquote]:before:w-ds-2 [&amp;_blockquote]:relative [&amp;_blockquote]:before:absolute [&amp;_blockquote]:before:-inset-y-0 [&amp;_blockquote]:before:start-0 [&amp;_blockquote]:before:content-[&quot;&quot;] [&amp;_em]:italic [&amp;_h1]:text-[2em] [&amp;_h2]:text-[1.55em] [&amp;_h3]:text-[1.33em] [&amp;_h4]:text-[1.11em] [&amp;_h5]:font-medium [&amp;_h6]:font-medium [&amp;_*:not(span)+*:not(span)]:mt-[1em] [&amp;_p+ol]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_p+ul]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_ol+p]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ol+ul]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ol+ol]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul+p]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul+ol]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul+ul]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul&gt;li+li]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_ul&gt;li]:break-words [&amp;_ul]:list-disc [&amp;_ol&gt;li+li]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_ol&gt;li::marker]:font-bold [&amp;_ol]:list-decimal [&amp;_a]:text-ds-purple-500 [&amp;_a:hover]:text-ds-purple-700 [&amp;_a:hover]:underline group-[.theme-set]/theme:[&amp;_a]:text-ds-brand [&amp;_ul]:ps-[1.5em] [&amp;_ol]:ps-[1.7em]"><p>Perpetual Derivatives are a type of Derivatives contract that have <strong>no expiration date</strong> and an <strong>auto-rolling</strong> feature <strong>every hour</strong>. </p><p>Perpetual contracts feature a funding rate, a payment between traders designed to keep the contract&#x27;s price aligned with the underlying asset&#x27;s spot price. More information on this mechanism can be found under &quot;Perpetual Contract Funding Rate Information&quot; in the next drop-down menu. </p><p><strong>Margin Class</strong> and maximum leverage by position size are detailed in <a target="blank" href="/articles/360022632452-derivatives-margin-schedule-maximum-leverage">Derivatives Margin Schedule &amp; Maximum Leverage</a>.</p><p><br/>Forex Perpetual (FX perps) information is detailed in <a target="blank" href="/articles/forex-perpetual-futures">Forex Perpetual Futures</a></p></div></div><div class="box-border w-full max-w-full overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out max-h-80"><div data-testid="notification-container" aria-labelledby="«R2iiplr7kq»" aria-described