global_search_section_futures":"Futures","field_global_search_section_most_popular":"Most popular global markets","field_global_search_section_newly_listed":"Newly listed crypto","field_global_search_section_popular_actions":"Popular actions","field_global_search_section_popular_categories":"Popular Categories","field_global_search_section_popular_markets":"Popular Markets","field_global_search_section_popular_searches":"Popular searches","field_global_search_section_popular_stocks":"Popular stocks","field_global_search_section_spot_margin_markets":"Spot & Margin","field_global_search_section_staking_earn":"Staking & Earn","field_global_search_section_stocks":"Stocks","field_global_search_section_support":"Support","field_global_search_section_top_category_assets":"Top {{category}} assets","field_global_search_staking_available_on":"Available on","field_global_search_staking_bonded":"Bonded","field_global_search_staking_bonded_time":"Bonded time","field_global_search_staking_explore_label":"Explore {{asset}}","field_global_search_staking_flexible":"Flexible","field_global_search_staking_payout":"Payout","field_global_search_staking_title":"Earn with {{asset}}","field_global_search_staking_weekly":"Weekly","field_global_search_subsection_etfs":"ETFs","field_global_search_subsection_stocks":"Stocks","field_global_search_subsection_xstocks":"xStocks","field_global_search_to_navigate_label":"to navigate","field_global_search_to_select_label":"to select","field_global_search_trigger_label":"Search","field_global_search_view_all":"View all","firstPublishedAt":"2026-01-19T14:03:59.892Z","lastPublishedAt":"2026-03-19T21:27:12.782Z","score":0}},"data":{"_createdAt":"2025-04-02T06:52:32Z","_id":"article-4844359082772","_system":{"base":{"id":"article-4844359082772","rev":"MwgZb85ftkde1TTvSxhsK8"}},"_type":"page","appId":"support","content_source_locale":"en_us","enabled_locales":[],"field_page_components":[{"_key":"295a203a6ebc","_type":"paragraphArticleLayout","field_article_breadcrumb_label":"Support","field_article_breadcrumbs":true,"field_children":[{"_key":"5d055e64d6ca","_type":"paragraphNotification","field_can_be_closed":false,"field_closed_state_is_persistent":true,"field_direction":"stacked","field_has_icon":true,"field_text":"\u003cp>Contract specifications for clients located in the European Economic Area (EEA) can be found \u003ca href=\"https://support.kraken.com/articles/perpetual-contract-specifications-for-clients-in-the-eea\" target=\"_blank\">here\u003c/a>.&nbsp;\u003c/p>\n","field_title":"Specifications for EEA clients:","field_tone":"primary"},{"_key":"f5adb07b4a52","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Below you can find four sections with detailed information on Kraken&#39;s linear Multi-M perpetual and fixed maturity derivatives contracts.\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>Click to expand each section:\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"7d533f2badf1","_type":"paragraphAccordion","field_children":[{"_key":"4b668ca2b1f0","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"b4eb252ed041","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Perpetual Derivatives are a type of Derivatives contract that have \u003cstrong>no expiration date\u003c/strong> and an \u003cstrong>auto-rolling\u003c/strong> feature \u003cstrong>every hour\u003c/strong>. \u003c/p>\u003cp>Perpetual contracts feature a funding rate, a payment between traders designed to keep the contract&#x27;s price aligned with the underlying asset&#x27;s spot price. More information on this mechanism can be found under &quot;Perpetual Contract Funding Rate Information&quot; in the next drop-down menu. \u003c/p>\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Margin Class\u003c/strong> and maximum leverage by position size are detailed in \u003ca href=\"/articles/360022632452-derivatives-margin-schedule-maximum-leverage\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Derivatives Margin Schedule &amp; Maximum Leverage\u003c/a>.\u003c/p>\u003cp>\u003cbr/>Forex Perpetual (FX perps) information is detailed in \u003ca href=\"/articles/forex-perpetual-futures\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">Forex Perpetual Futures\u003c/a>\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"d979cd789449","_type":"paragraphNotification","field_alternative_icon":"InfoCircle","field_can_be_closed":false,"field_direction":"inline","field_has_icon":true,"field_text":"\u003cp>\u003cp>Delisted and settled contracts are archived \u003ca href=\"/articles/7526425887508-Futures-contracts-trading-suspensions-delistings\" >here\u003c/a>. \u003c/p>\u003c/p>","field_title":"Please note:","field_tone":"primary"},{"_key":"b678f6195c48","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTable","field_rows":[{"_key":"biioCkHhBRC5Hs4sHeMGX","field_cells":[{"_key":"cIFCHu5cJWmRDDhtzSpEf","cell_description":"Content of Column 1","field_content":"Symbol"},{"_key":"42czOPT_rQkrugoBzi5AF","cell_description":"Content of Column 2","field_content":"Base Currency"},{"_key":"QsWGC6w5rdtKVLqRU2ITg","cell_description":"Content of Column 3","field_content":"Min Lot"},{"_key":"0-tAgLB-mwku33vDJYjpG","cell_description":"Content of Column 4","field_content":"Tick Size"},{"_key":"-4R9CmXft5EHJHKqhyOiu","cell_description":"Content of Column 5","field_content":"\u003cdiv class=\"softmerge-inner\" style=\"width:97px;left:-1px\">Max Position (Base)\u003c/div>"},{"_key":"QuiQZW00oJQUSoBxSn3LL","cell_description":"Content of Column 6","field_content":"\u003cdiv class=\"softmerge-inner\" style=\"width:97px;left:-1px\">Margin Class &amp; Max Leverage\u003c/div>"},{"_key":"k7txLwgJnQGGUtFkhyGS0","cell_description":"Content of Column 7","field_content":"First Trading"}],"row_description":"Row :: Symbol"},{"_key":"bgg3hpe12oor4QwsT9yZm","field_cells":[{"_key":"RiO8xW9hrc6kSX-9oehiC","cell_description":"Content of Column 1","field_content":"\u003ca target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://pro.kraken.com/app/trade/futures-1inch-usd-perp\">PF_1INCHUSD\u003c/a>"},{"_key":"zQ79l_F-G7PYpVMHdxh6G","cell_description":"Content of Column 2","field_content":"1inch (1INC