t Contract Platform":{"name":"Smart Contract Platform","cg_name":"Smart Contract Platform"},"Decentralized Science (DeSci)":{"name":"DeSci","cg_name":"Decentralized Science (DeSci)"},"Bitcoin Sidechains":{"name":"Bitcoin Sidechains","cg_name":"Bitcoin Sidechains"},"Privacy":{"name":"Privacy","cg_name":"Privacy","icon":"ShieldTick"},"Entertainment":{"name":"Entertainment","cg_name":"Entertainment"},"Cosmos Ecosystem":{"name":"Cosmos Ecosystem","cg_name":"Cosmos Ecosystem"},"Cat-Themed":{"name":"Cat Meme","cg_name":"Cat-Themed"},"Ethereum Ecosystem":{"name":"Ethereum Ecosystem","cg_name":"Ethereum Ecosystem"},"Optimism Ecosystem":{"name":"Optimism Ecosystem","cg_name":"Optimism Ecosystem"},"Polygon Ecosystem":{"name":"Polygon Ecosystem","cg_name":"Polygon Ecosystem"},"Solana Ecosystem":{"name":"Solana Ecosystem","cg_name":"Solana Ecosystem"},"Avalanche Ecosystem":{"name":"Avalanche Ecosystem","cg_name":"Avalanche Ecosystem"},"NFT":{"name":"NFT","cg_name":"NFT","icon":"Nft"},"Derivatives":{"name":"Derivatives","cg_name":"Derivatives"},"Dog-Themed":{"name":"Dog Meme","cg_name":"Dog-Themed"},"Arbitrum Ecosystem":{"name":"Arbitrum Ecosystem","cg_name":"Arbitrum Ecosystem"},"Zero Knowledge (ZK)":{"name":"Zero knowledge","cg_name":"Zero Knowledge (ZK)"},"Base Ecosystem":{"name":"Base Ecosystem","cg_name":"Base Ecosystem"},"Sports":{"name":"Sports","cg_name":"Sports"},"Algorand Ecosystem":{"name":"Algorand Ecosystem","cg_name":"Algorand Ecosystem"},"Bitcoin Ecosystem":{"name":"Bitcoin Ecosystem","cg_name":"Bitcoin Ecosystem"}}},"path":"/articles/4844359082772-linear-multi-collateral-derivatives-contract-specifications","resolvedUrlWithoutQueryParams":"/articles/4844359082772-linear-multi-collateral-derivatives-contract-specifications","dynamicAssets":{"resolvedDynamicVariables":{},"resolvedDynamicVariablesDataEntryKeys":{}},"dynamicVariables":{},"i18n":{"lowerCaseLng":false,"lng":"en-US","fallbackLng":"en-US","resources":{"en-US":{"translation":{"config_header_support][field_app_download_button_label":"Get the Kraken app","config_header_support][field_qr_code_desktop_label":"Get the Kraken app","config_header_support][field_qr_code_mobile_label":"Buy crypto in minutes","config_header_support][f8db732fda43][title":"My Activities","config_header_support][cf2a53d6c542][title":"Log in","config_header_support][68678992b80d][title":"Sign up","config_footer_support][81cd05ed1062][title":"Privacy Notice","config_footer_support][2f82199676b9][title":"Terms of Service","config_footer_support][ec191f16c6ad][title":"Terms of Service","config_footer_support][f05604a921a6][title":"Cookie Settings","config_footer_support][832f81bec517][title":"Candidate Privacy Notice","config_footer_support][bebccdef75b1][title":"Disclosures","config_footer_support][99e4e0a788d9][title":"Disclosures","config_footer_support][3a275cdc8af8][title":"Exchange Trading Rules","config_footer_support][58d046d8a1e2][title":"Compliance Hub","config_footer_support][c1bda693e58e][title":"Do Not Sell/Share","config_footer_support][field_copyrightnotice][field_privacy_statement":"© 2011 - {YYYY} Payward, Inc.","config_footer_support][66bc85ffb4ce][field_body":"\u003cp>This page is for Kraken Global. Please visit \u003ca href=\"https://blog.kraken.com/japan\">blog.kraken.com/japan\u003c/a> for information on services, documents and notices for customers residing in Japan.\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>&nbsp;\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Important notice about crypto asset trading\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>Crypto assets are not a national currency in or outside of Japan. Because the price of crypto assets can fluctuate, there is a possibility of loss. If the private keys are lost, you may completely lose access to the corresponding crypto assets and their value may be lost.&nbsp;Breakdowns in the blockchain transfer mechanism could cause crypto assets to lose their value. Crypto assets can be used to pay for goods only when the seller has consented to accepting crypto assets as consideration.&nbsp;When trading crypto assets, please understand the transaction details completely and proceed at your own discretion.\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>&nbsp;\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Important notice about Staking service\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>The Staking service is a loan transaction of crypto assets based on a crypto asset loan for consumption agreement. This does NOT mean that clients perform staking on their own. Crypto assets borrowed by us are not subject to segregation management since this activity does not fall under a Crypto Asset Exchange activity under the Payment Services Law. This service is not covered by deposit insurance. Reward rates&nbsp; (Usage Fee on the&nbsp; Loan for Consumption Agreement) reflect the annual percentage rate (APR). All reward rates are estimates subject to change. When using the Staking service, please understand the transaction details completely by reading &ldquo;Terms and Conditions of Crypto Asset Loan for Consumption Agreement&rdquo; and &ldquo;Transaction Manual for Crypto Asset Loan for Consumption Agreement&rdquo;, and proceed at your own discretion.\u003c/p>\n","config_footer_support][f455b61b6085][field_body":"\u003cp>\u003c/p>\u003cp>Payward Europe Solutions Limited, trading as Kraken, is regulated by the Central Bank of Ireland. Payward Global Solutions Limited, trading as Kraken, is regulated by the Central Bank of Ireland. Registered office: 70 Sir John Rogerson’s Quay, Dublin, D02 R296, Ireland. Click \u003ca target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.kraken.com/legal/micar\">here\u003c/a> for related policies and disclosures.\u003c/p>","config_footer_support][d77d90ef8ff5][field_body":"\u003cp>These materials are for general information purposes only and are not investment or financial product advice or a recommendation or solicitation to buy, sell, stake or hold any cryptoasset or to engage in any specific trading strategy. Kraken does not and will not work to increase or decrease the price of any particular cryptoasset it makes available. The unpredictable nature of the crypto-asset markets can lead to loss of funds. Tax may be payable on any return and/or on any increase in the value of your cryptoassets and you should seek independent advice on your taxation position. Geographic restrictions may apply. Some crypto products and markets are unregulated. Kraken’s regulatory status for its various products and services differs per jurisdiction and you may not be protected by government compensation and/or regulatory protection schemes. See Legal Disclosures for each jurisdiction (\u003ca target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://www.kraken.com/legal/disclosures\">here\u003c/a>).\u003c/p>","config_footer_support][c27ce58cd219][field_body":"\u003cp>\u003c/p>\u003cp>Payward Canada Inc., operating as Kraken, is registered as a money services business with FINTRAC (M19343731) and as a Restricted Dealer with the Ontario Securities Commission and the securities regulators in each of the provinces and territories of Canada.\u003c/p>","config_footer_support][0f2d2902d103][field_body":"\u003cp>La inversión en criptoactivos no está regulada, puede no ser adecuada para inversores minoristas y perderse la totalidad del importe invertido. Es importante leer y comprender los riesgos de esta inversión que se explican detalladamente en esta ubicación. Las rentabilidades pasadas no constituyen un indicador fiable de las rentabilidades futuras.\u003c/p>","config_footer_support][d67bcbb3426d][field_body":"\u003cp>Kraken Derivatives is only available to persons who are wholesale clients. Any financial products described in, or services that may be referred to or provided in connection with, this page or any other Kraken Derivatives page are not made available to any person who is a ‘retail client’. The information provided about the Kraken Derivatives service is not intended to be distributed or passed on, directly or indirectly, to any class of persons in Australia other than wholesale clients.\u003c/p>","config_footer_support][f2143759a106][field_body":"\u003cp>\u003c/p>\u003cp>Beaufort Fiduciaries Pty Ltd (ACN 162 139 871, AFSL 545124) is the AFS licensee and a VASP-TBC. Bit Trade Pty Ltd (ACN 163 237 634) a VASP-TBC and an Authorised Representative (AR 001312156) of Beaufort Fiduciaries. Registered office: Unit 610, 478 George St, Sydney NSW 2000. | FSG | PDS | TMD | Complaints / AFCA | Privacy | Terms | Scamwatch\u003c/p>","config_footer_support][03390c584cc7][title":"Margin Trading","config_footer_support][124920a363ad][title":"{{\"Derivatives Trading\" if (countryCode | lower) in [\"de\"] else \"Futures Trading\"}}","config_footer_support][8cbae9290836][title":"OTC Trading","config_footer_support][e6eac992e16f][title":"Institutions","config_footer_support][2f220c38a494][title":"API Trading","config_footer_support][848c8e3fb9c0][title":"Kraken API center","config_footer_support][8fa420f93387][title":"Staking Rewards","config_footer_support][c74c7ce9e6c4][title":"Send Money","config_footer_support][706406a3952e][title":"Recurring buys","config_footer_support][d364d32a56f8][title":"Buy Crypto","config_footer_support][a3d869b55a85][title":"Sell Crypto","config_footer_support][074407394d1b][title":"Features","config_footer_support][a67e29bf2dea][title":"Kraken Security","config_footer_support][de8827476624][title":"Kraken Careers","config_footer_support][91fb10bbf930][title":"Kraken Blog","config_footer_support][fa00ceb70535][title":"Kraken Developer","config_footer_support][13da005cad8c][title":"Press Room","config_footer_support][2a397178a494][title":"Affiliate Program","config_footer_support][c699fd9fba23][title":"Asset Listings","config_footer_support][44929307cd92][title":"Kraken Status","config_footer_support][d8f624df2141][title":"Support Center","config_footer_support][8d45504e80fd][title":"Complaints","config_footer_support][240e4bdac384][title":"Breakout Prop Trading","