search_facade][field_global_search_subsection_etfs":"ETFs","config_globalsearch_facade][field_global_search_subsection_stocks":"Stocks","config_globalsearch_facade][field_global_search_subsection_xstocks":"xStocks","config_globalsearch_facade][field_global_search_to_navigate_label":"to navigate","config_globalsearch_facade][field_global_search_to_select_label":"to select","config_globalsearch_facade][field_global_search_trigger_label":"Search","config_globalsearch_facade][field_global_search_view_all":"View all","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][field_page_meta][description":"Support Center for Kraken.com | Bitcoin & Cryptocurrency Exchange | Bitcoin Trading Platform","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][field_page_meta][title":"Linear Multi-Collateral Derivatives Contract Specifications | Kraken","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][295a203a6ebc][field_article_breadcrumb_label":"Support","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][5d055e64d6ca][field_text":"\u003cp>Contract specifications for clients located in the European Economic Area (EEA) can be found \u003ca href=\"https://support.kraken.com/articles/perpetual-contract-specifications-for-clients-in-the-eea\" target=\"_blank\">here\u003c/a>.&nbsp;\u003c/p>\n","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][5d055e64d6ca][field_title":"Specifications for EEA clients:","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][f5adb07b4a52][field_body":"\u003cp>Below you can find four sections with detailed information on Kraken&#39;s linear Multi-M perpetual and fixed maturity derivatives contracts.\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>Click to expand each section:\u003c/p>\n","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][b4eb252ed041][field_body":"\u003cp>Perpetual Derivatives are a type of Derivatives contract that have \u003cstrong>no expiration date\u003c/strong> and an \u003cstrong>auto-rolling\u003c/strong> feature \u003cstrong>every hour\u003c/strong>. \u003c/p>\u003cp>Perpetual contracts feature a funding rate, a payment between traders designed to keep the contract&#x27;s price aligned with the underlying asset&#x27;s spot price. More information on this mechanism can be found under &quot;Perpetual Contract Funding Rate Information&quot; in the next drop-down menu. \u003c/p>\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Margin Class\u003c/strong> and maximum leverage by position size are detailed in \u003ca href=\"/articles/360022632452-derivatives-margin-schedule-maximum-leverage\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Derivatives Margin Schedule &amp; Maximum Leverage\u003c/a>.\u003c/p>\u003cp>\u003cbr/>Forex Perpetual (FX perps) information is detailed in \u003ca href=\"/articles/forex-perpetual-futures\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">Forex Perpetual Futures\u003c/a>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][d979cd789449][field_text":"\u003cp>\u003cp>Delisted and settled contracts are archived \u003ca href=\"/articles/7526425887508-Futures-contracts-trading-suspensions-delistings\" >here\u003c/a>. \u003c/p>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][d979cd789449][field_title":"Please note:","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][cifchu5cjwmrddhtzspef][field_content":"Symbol","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][42czopt_rqkrugobzi5af][field_content":"Base Currency","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][qswgc6w5rdtkvlqru2itg][field_content":"Min Lot","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][0-taglb-mwku33vdjyjpg][field_content":"Tick Size","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][-4r9cmxft5ehjhkqhyoiu][field_content":"\u003cdiv class=\"softmerge-inner\" style=\"width:97px;left:-1px\">Max Position (Base)\u003c/div>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][qui