liqa (ZIL)","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][fx4umctlopbpj69iba8xu][field_content":"10","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][h9njd6jtgf2iwlrnnoutq][field_content":"0.000001","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][ziqx0alskgclvbny5ssnc][field_content":"146,900,000","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][s6h99slbu9aavy3ftutxp][field_content":"Class E (10x)","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][jh58wqj8d4r338sbyleqf][field_content":"26-Nov-2024","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][0g6w5lh_m0ydwtj1dozgz][field_content":"\u003ca target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://pro.kraken.com/app/trade/futures-zk-usd-perp\">PF_ZKUSD\u003c/a>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][vn_gwzmgdtqf_otk3m764][field_content":"ZKsync (ZK)","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][cst_okcrg3adiymx94pir][field_content":"1","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][dwq0h8uvbr2b935mo_qtu][field_content":"0.000001","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][hbae7-lpzaqhmnd494xjj][field_content":"40,000,000","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][bvtlqncz48z_cabho7tf0][field_content":"Class C (25x)","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][be8o8xkknfmj0ltfouxy8][field_content":"01-Aug-2024","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][pdc7gjpudt5c1yejm-1wr][field_content":"\u003ca target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://pro.kraken.com/app/trade/futures-zro-usd-perp\">PF_ZROUSD\u003c/a>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][gog8woc5mqoeq1b21wzei][field_content":"LayerZero (ZRO)","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][ifbit5nudbyma3rv98re8][field_content":"1","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][k7jejiflqzpfxgfa6_w_q][field_content":"0.0001","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][fdztnhxk6oxfyk-clsdsr][field_content":"1,000,000","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][lq8c-gandhmklo6xoq-ce][field_content":"Class C (25x)","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][zq5fkubixymtuaiejlfji][field_content":"21-Jun-2024","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][pedofobjhaiveuxd6xpdi][field_content":"\u003ca target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://pro.kraken.com/app/trade/futures-zrx-usd-perp\">PF_ZRXUSD\u003c/a>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][sohnsigp1eg9xogn1m-za][field_content":"\u003cdiv class=\"softmerge-inner\" style=\"width:97px;left:-1px\">0x Protocol (ZRX)\u003c/div>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][wef2zwvmavyz2xzswhuiq][field_content":"1","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][dpy3citme1mnbtvw7g8yp][field_content":"0.00001","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][vo89vwsane5d4uh6vpbo2][field_content":"10,000,000","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][a-gyxx4pofv6bnrznoqzl][field_content":"Class E (10x)","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][ui5_sidnpqvegjmacmdda][field_content":"12-Apr-2023","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][b678f6195c48][field_search_placeholder":"Search","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][a186b42fcfd2][field_body":"\u003cp>*BTC is used on the platform UI. XBT is used on the API and account logs. Both refer to Bitcoin (BTC).\u003c/p>\u003cp>**These contracts are not available on the \u003ca href=\"https://futures.kraken.com\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">legacy user interface\u003c/a> and can only be accessed via Kraken Pro \u003ca href=\"https://pro.kraken.com/app/trade\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">web\u003c/a> or \u003ca href=\"/articles/360049788312-Kraken-Pro-mobile-app-frequently-asked-questions-\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\">mobile\u003c/a> and \u003ca href=\"https://docs.kraken.com/api/\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">API\u003c/a>. \u003c/p>\u003cp>Contract specification changes are published on our \u003ca href=\"/articles/13049711807636-derivatives-platform-parameters-changelog\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Derivatives Platform Parameters Changelog\u003c/a>.\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][4b668ca2b1f0][field_faq_answer":"\u003cp>Perpetual Derivatives are a type of Derivatives contract that have \u003cstrong>no expiration date\u003c/strong> and an \u003cstrong>auto-rolling\u003c/strong> feature \u003cstrong>every hour\u003c/strong>. \u003c/p>\u003cp>Perpetual contracts feature a funding rate, a payment between traders designed to keep the contract&#x27;s price aligned with the underlying asset&#x27;s spot price. More information on this mechanism can be found under &quot;Perpetual Contract Funding Rate Information&quot; in the next drop-down menu. \u003c/p>\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Margin Class\u003c/strong> and maximum leverage by position size are detailed in \u003ca href=\"/articles/360022632452-derivatives-margin-schedule-maximum-leverage\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Derivatives Margin Schedule &amp; Maximum Leverage\u003c/a>.\u003c/p>\u003cp>\u003cbr/>Forex Perpetual (FX perps) information is detailed in \u003ca href=\"/articles/forex-perpetual-futures\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">Forex Perpetual Futures\u003c/a>\u003c/p>\n\u003cblockquote>\u003cstrong>Please note:\u003c/strong> \u003cp>\u003cp>Delisted and settled contracts are archived \u003ca href=\"/articles/7526425887508-Futures-contracts-trading-suspensions-delistings\" >here\u003c/a>. \u003c/p>\u003c/p>\u003c/blockquote>\n\u003ctable>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003c/table>\n\u003cp>*BTC is used on the platform UI. XBT is used on the API and account logs. Both refer to Bitcoin (BTC).\u003c/p>\u003cp>**These contracts are not available on the \u003ca href=\"https://futures.kraken.com\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">legacy user interface\u003c/a> and can only be accessed via Kraken Pro \u003ca href=\"https://pro.kraken.com/app/trade\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">web\u003c/a> or \u003ca href=\"/articles/360049788312-Kraken-Pro-mobile-app-frequently-asked-questions-\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\">mobile\u003c/a> and \u003ca href=\"https://docs.kraken.com/api/\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">API\u003c/a>. \u003c/p>\u003cp>Contract specification changes are published on our \u003ca href=\"/articles/13049711807636-derivatives-platform-parameters-changelog\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Derivatives Platform Parameters Changelog\u003c/a>.\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][4b668ca2b1f0][field_title":"Perpetual Contract Specifications","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][277037867b91][field_body":"\u003cp>Perpetual Derivatives are a type of Derivatives contract that have \u003cstrong>no expiration date\u003c/strong> and an \u003cstrong>auto-rolling\u003c/strong> feature \u003cstrong>every hour\u003c/strong>. \u003c/p>\u003cp>Perpetual contracts feature a funding rate, a payment between traders designed to keep the contract&#x27;s price aligned with the underlying asset&#x27;s spot price. \u003c/p>\u003cp>If the funding rate is positive, long positions pay short positions; if negative, short positions pay long positions. \u003c/p>\u003cp>Traders may pay or receive funding dependent on market conditions. The price difference is calculated hourly, with funding adjustments reflected as unrealized profit or loss, settling at the end of each hour or when the net position changes.\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][8efb77260ebf][field_content":"\u003cp>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][295461d06f4e][field_content":"\u003cp>Additional Information\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][13d61a8ca097][field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Auto-Roll Period\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][b16172ac421d][field_content":"\u003cp>Every 1 hour at the end of the hour\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][02f6e42e441a][field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Rate-setting Calculation Window\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][aca4d7268612][field_content":"\u003cp>Rate for next period is calculated over current 1-hour period (e.g., rate for 12-13 UTC period is calculated in window between 11-12 UTC)\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][84cca0d3deb5][field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Funding Rate\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][faf5c3bbf592][field_content":"\u003cp>Between start and end of the Rate-setting Period the Funding Rate is computed as the time-weighted average premium, and standardised to a per-hour basis. Permissible range per 1 hours: [-0.5%, +0.5%]*** (i.e., 800 basis point magnitude for 8-hour realisation period)\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][12f56c554dd4][field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Payout Frequency\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][f60235fe5a37][field_content":"\u003cp>Continuously based on \u003cstrong>Funding Rate\u003c/strong> set at the end of the prior \u003cstrong>Funding Period\u003c/strong>. Positions will immediately and continuously receive or send funding while open in the perpetual contracts. The funding accumulates as unrealised profit/loss and settles every 1 hour at end of the \u003cstrong>Funding Period\u003c/strong>, or when user changes net open position (whichever occurs first).\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][71f4ba99ce29][field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Funding Rate Multiplier\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][06d4f1ef0171][field_content":"\u003cp>n = 8 This is the coefficient used in the calculation of the funding rate. A value of 1/n means that, ceteris paribus, it will take n hours to realise the Average Premium. Example: if the Average Premium is 0.36% for the 1-hour period, then Funding Rate is equal to 0.045%, meaning that over the course of 8 hours, this 0.36% total will be realized.\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][bc452025528a][field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Funding Rate Calculation\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][8ee1a984f4dd][field_content":"\u003cp>In a given 1-hour Funding Period, \u003cstrong>Premium\u003c/strong> values calculated from minutely perpetual contract prices (60 observations) using an \u003cstrong>Impact Mid\u003c/strong> are recorded versus the \u003cstrong>Real Time Platform Ticker\u003c/strong>. The \u003cstrong>Impact Mid\u003c/strong> is the median of the average entry price market-selling x value of contracts and market-buying x value of contracts. See table above for contract-specific values. The \u003cstrong>Average Premium\u003c/strong> is calculated as the average of the mid 30 values recorded from the above 60 observations. Finally, this value is weighted by the \u003cstrong>Funding Rate Multiplier\u003c/strong>. If \u003cstrong>Average Premium\u003c/strong> is greater than 0 for the 1 hour period, those in Long positions will continuously pay out to Short positions, which pushes the price closer to Index. If \u003cstrong>Average Premium\u003c/strong> is less than 0 for the 1 hour period, those in Short positions will continuously pay out to Long positions, which pushes the price closer to Index.\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][270a0576dc13][field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Trading Hours\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][6e43bb0cce31][field_content":"\u003cp>24 hours/day, 7 days/week, 365 days/year (excluding \u003ca href=\"/articles/360022837571-Platform-outage-options\" >maintenance\u003c/a>)\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][b941f16aaf10][field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>P&amp;L Settlement Method\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][117d520a43f7][field_content":"\u003cp>Cash settled in USD with optional payout in any of the \u003ca href=\"/articles/4843323030164-Futures-Collateral-Currencies\" >collateral currencies\u003c/a> (profit only, losses are always realised in USD)\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][0b1e14944e49][field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Fee Structure\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][2cac635b1f2d][field_content":"\u003cp>Kraken Derivatives uses a maker-taker \u003ca href=\"/articles/360048917612-Fee-schedule\" >fee structure\u003c/a>. Fees are calculated as a percentage of the notional order value for a matched trade. No fees are charged on auto-roll or funding payouts -- these occur strictly between counter-parties.\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][f5ed382e7e70][field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Contract Expiration\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][b46d825d1a69][field_content":"\u003cp>The perpetual derivatives are non-expiring, which means that positions in the contract are never “expired” or “matured”, however there is a settlement process every hour that applies funding to anchor the spot value to the Index. See \u003cstrong>Last Trading\u003c/strong> for more information.\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][98d4e973dd45][field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Settlement time\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][865d82cde50d][field_content":"\u003cp>Every 1 hour at the end of the hour: The accumulated unrealised funding is settled and new rate set based on TWAP premium to index in prior rate period.\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][fbbb54332e08][field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Last Trading\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][2f8a74c01afc][field_content":"\u003cp>This contract remains trading perpetually and would only expire in an emergency situation if Kraken Derivatives deems necessary to settle/expire the contract. Kraken Derivatives reserve the right to set any contract to post-only, suspended, or settle any contract at any time and without warning due to either adverse market conditions or regulatory risk. \u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][c275ebbc8d1f][field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Initial Margin\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][8fea15572baa][field_content":"\u003cp>\u003ca href=\"/articles/360022632452-Margin-Schedule\" >As low as 2%\u003c/a>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][000d2eb6525a][field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Maintenance Margin\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][32cab3455d6e][field_content":"\u003cp>Half of Initial Margin\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][ed514357cd47][field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Maximum Initial Leverage\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][643fe7df3c69][field_content":"\u003cp>\u003ca href=\"/articles/360022632452-Margin-Schedule\" >Up to 50x\u003c/a>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][26fae5bc048d][field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Mark Price\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][c5c632c63e08][field_content":"\u003cp>Index Price plus the 30 seconds exponential moving average of the order book mid price minus the index price (future&#x27;s basis). The premium for perpetual contracts is capped at 1%. Calculation: Index Price + EMA_30seconds(Impact Mid Price - Index Price) \u003cbr/> \u003cstrong>Note\u003c/strong>: in the extremely rare circumstance that the Index Price is unavailable for whatever reason, the above caps may not apply and the Mark Price will be equal to the Impact Mid Price.\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][fe86707a63ce][field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Margin &amp; Settlement Currency\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][21a12c713b92][field_content":"\u003cp>USD, but with full collateral options of BTC, ETH, ADA, DOT, LTC, SOL, XRP, USDT, USDC, EUR, and GBP, adjusted for haircut (see \u003ca href=\"/articles/4843323030164\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">Derivatives Collateral Currencies\u003c/a>)\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][6ae9d96ca106][field_search_placeholder":"Search","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][a2acfa44ebff][field_heading":" The funding rate for a given perpetual contract is represented in two different ways: ","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][7d2fc3324afb][field_body":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>absolute rate\u003c/strong>: The amount of funding an account will receive by maintaining a 1 contract unit short position for 1 hour. This is more useful for account log purposes.\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][8d2063e45b08][field_body":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>absolute funding payout\u003c/strong> = # of contracts * absolute funding rate * time elapsed within funding period without position alteration\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][1b01ba50e89a][field_body":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>relative rate\u003c/strong>: The absolute funding rate relative to the spot price at the time of funding rate calculation. This is an intermediate value in the calculation of the absolute funding rate and is the number we display in the front end (as a %) as the &#x27;funding rate&#x27;.\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][c181afb5cf7c][field_body":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>relative funding payout\u003c/strong> = # of contracts * (relative funding rate*spot price) * time elapsed within funding period without position alteration\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][4458b967a6ff][field_body":"\u003cp>In order to get a complete understanding of the funding rate dynamics of the Perpetual Contract, we present examples to demonstrate the key features.\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][4458b967a6ff][field_heading":" Funding Rate Examples ","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][2813e299161c][field_body":"\u003cp>Assume time is 12 UTC and that the price of BTC is $37,000 (via bitcoin-dollar real-time index) and the Perpetual trades at $37,100 the whole time until 13 UTC. The average premium is computed as 0.27027% for the 1-hour period (100/37,000). This leads to a funding rate of 0.27027 / 8 = 0.03378375% per hour.\u003c/p>\u003cp>Now assume that you are in a short position of 2 BTC, with 1 BTC perpetual contract valued at $37,100. If you hold this position from 13 to 14 UTC, and the premium in the 13 to 14 UTC period remains as 0.27027%, then you will be paid funding of 25.0 USD for the one-hour period [(2*37000)*0.0003378375]\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][dee2c9f7d08c][field_body":"\u003cp>Assume time is 12 UTC and that price of BTC is $37,000 and the Perpetual trades at $39,700 until 13 UTC. The average premium is computed as 7.297297% for the 1-hour period. This leads to a funding rate of 7.297297 / 8 = 0.91216213% per hour. \u003c/p>\u003cp>The maximum funding rate per hour in any given period is 0.50%. The minimum is -0.50%.  \u003c/p>\u003cp>As a result, this 0.91216213% hourly rate is floored to 0.50% per hour, so that the maximum \u003cem>8\u003c/em> hour realization will not exceed 4%. \u003c/p>\u003cp>Note that there is no \"dampening\" of rates done in this model: if a 1 hour computed rate is near 0, then it will pay out non-0 value even if it is de minimis.\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][0960e466738d][field_body":"\u003cp>Assume time is 13 UTC and that the index spot price of BTCUSD is $37,000, and the relative rate set for the 1 hour period is 0.05% per hour.\u003cbr/> \u003c/p>\u003cp>Now assume the time is 13:30 UTC and the perpetual trades at $38,000 and you enter a Short position of 4 BTC at this price.\u003cbr/> \u003c/p>\u003cp>You will immediately begin receiving funding at an absolute rate of 0.05%*$37,000 = 18.5 USD per hour per unit.\u003cbr/>\u003c/p>\u003cp>In your available balance you will then see this rate applying in your unrealised PnL through continuous funding payout equal to:\u003c/p>\u003cp>\u003cem>18.5 * 4 BTC = $74 per hour\u003c/em>\u003c/p>\u003cp>\u003cem>$1.233 per minute\u003c/em>\u003c/p>\u003cp>\u003c/p>\u003cp>This will pay out continuously until 14 UTC where the relative funding rate will change based on the market activity between 13-14 UTC.\u003cbr/> \u003c/p>\u003cp>In your 4 BTC short position at the end of the half hour period you will have $36.99 applied in your account log at 14 UTC.\u003cbr/> \u003c/p>\u003cp>Assume this new relative funding rate is now 0.03% and the real-time spot index is $37,900 for BTCUSD at 14 UTC. \u003cbr/> \u003c/p>\u003cp>From 14 UTC to 15 UTC a new absolute funding rate will begin applying of 0.03%*$37,900=$11.37 per hour per unit.\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][3ffb3ff37f22][field_body":"\u003cp>Assume time is 14 UTC and you enter a position long 2 BTC on BTCUSD at 37,000. Assume that the funding rate for the one-hour period (13-14 UTC) is set as -0.04% per hour.\u003cbr/> \u003c/p>\u003cp>At 15 UTC, after you have held this position for one full hour, you will have earned $29.6 [(0.0004*2 BTC)*37,000], which credits continuously throughout the hour period you hold it.\u003cbr/> \u003c/p>\u003cp>However, during this period, the price was at a premium and so the new one-hour rate set for 14 - 15 UTC is 0.04% per hour. After one hour of holding the position, you have paid $29.6 and you close at 16 UTC.\u003cbr/> \u003c/p>\u003cp>Your funding for the two hour period you held the position is thus + $29.6 for the first period and then - $29.6 for the first second and your net flows are 0 for this.\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][b17142f788bf][field_body":"\u003cp>Assume it&#x27;s 12 UTC you are in a 5 BTC long position on BTCUSD with spot index at $37,000 and the rate in the funding period is -0.08%. This credits and debits every millisecond to every user with an open position. It credits first as unrealised profit and loss, but you have the funds available right away to use in further positions or transfer into your Cash account. The funding is booked into your account log and realised when one of the following events occur:\u003cbr/>\u003c/p>\u003cp>- You adjust your open position up or down by any amount, \u003c/p>\u003cp>-You hold until the end of the Funding Period, at which point it is booked (occurs at the end of every hour).\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][ceda06f5ca7e][field_body":"\u003cp>Assume it&#x27;s 12 UTC you are in a 3 BTC long position on PF_BTCUSD with spot index at $37,000 and the rate in the funding period is -0.05%. Assume that you have set your profit currency as ETH and you hold this position until the end of the funding period at 13 UTC.\u003cbr/>\u003c/p>\u003cp>0.0015*37,000*3 = $55.5 per hour\u003cbr/>\u003c/p>\u003cp>At the end of the period at 13 UTC, assume that the price of ETH is 2,500 (from the ether-dollar real-time index)\u003cbr/>\u003c/p>\u003cp>The conversion can be calculated using the following:\u003cbr/>= Amount in USD to be converted / (Target currency index * (1 - 0.25%))\u003cbr/>= 55.5 USD / (2,500 ETHUSD * .9975)\u003cbr/>= 0.022 ETH\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][d39992643fbf][field_title":"Perpetual Contract Funding Rate Information","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][8634678dff36][field_content":"\u003cp>Symbol\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][a8e125b62833][field_content":"\u003cp>Active Maturities\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][b259b09eda5e][field_content":"\u003cp>Base Currency\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][7d98c79fdafb][field_content":"\u003cp>Min Order\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][00ec0ac1470e][field_content":"\u003cp>Tick Size\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][4643204c73aa][field_content":"\u003cp>Max Position (Base units)\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][892d857639ee][field_content":"\u003cp>Margin Class\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][741630c57768][field_content":"\u003cp>Settlement Index\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][e2d8f5d77eee][field_content":"\u003cp>FF_ETHUSD\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][d284c3814d78][field_content":"\u003cp>Weekly, Monthly, Quarterly, Semiannual\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][10c9c9eb21bb][field_content":"\u003cp>Ethereum (ETH)\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][2b2d1ae7f539][field_content":"\u003cp>0.001\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][658cb1831caa][field_content":"\u003cp>0.1\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][4346dd044438][field_content":"\u003cp>8,000\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][ee4ec4d8c7d1][field_content":"\u003cp>Class A\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][e48974850195][field_content":"\u003cp>ETHOPTRR\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][6ffcb006ce32][field_content":"\u003cp>FF_SOLUSD\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][d635c2af251e][field_content":"\u003cp>Monthly, Quarterly\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][c13acc63dc14][field_content":"\u003cp>Solana (SOL)\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][ef708bed713a][field_content":"\u003cp>0.01\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][2ff7c1890e5e][field_content":"\u003cp>0.01\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][1f07a239c6ab][field_content":"\u003cp>80,000\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][02f75665afbd][field_content":"\u003cp>Class B\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][8f65f3d14784][field_content":"\u003cp>SOLOPTRR\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][dfa0cd788cb3][field_content":"\u003cp>FF_XBTUSD*\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][ae59b3ba739b][field_content":"\u003cp>Weekly, Monthly, Quarterly, Semiannual\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][8223a13e9f36][field_content":"\u003cp>Bitcoin (BTC*)\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][f2f1525d71ff][field_content":"\u003cp>0.0001\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][8bb9400837d9][field_content":"\u003cp>1\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][c2db1af79436][field_content":"\u003cp>600\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][308dfe7af6db][field_content":"\u003cp>Class A\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][f20097d1f5fb][field_content":"\u003cp>BTCOPTRR\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][a9558a7c3508][field_search_placeholder":"Search","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][4b616971b09e][field_body":"\u003cp>*BTC is used on the platform UI. XBT is used on the API and account logs. Both refer to Bitcoin (BTC).\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][1541ac5174d6][field_body":"\u003cblockquote>\u003cstrong>PnL Settlement Method &amp; Collateral Currencies:\u003c/strong> Linear Derivatives are settled in USD by default, or your chosen profit currency. See\u003ca href=\"/articles/4843323030164-Futures-Collateral-Currencies\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\"> Derivatives Collateral Currencies\u003c/a> for more information.\u003c/blockquote>\u003cp>\u003c/p>\u003cblockquote>\u003cstrong>Trading Hours: \u003c/strong>24 hours/day, 7 days/week, 365 days/year (excluding maintenance)\u003c/blockquote>\u003cp>\u003c/p>\u003cblockquote>\u003cstrong>Fee Structure: \u003c/strong>Kraken Derivatives uses a \u003ca href=\"/articles/360048917612-Fee-schedule\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">maker-taker fee structure.\u003c/a> Fees are calculated as a percentage of the notional order value for a matched trade. Holding a position until settlement will result in a taker fee. \u003cbr/>\u003cbr/>Conversion fees and interest may be applied in some instances. See\u003ca href=\"/articles/4844392809620-Fees-Charges-for-Multi-Collateral-Futures\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\"> Fees &amp; Charges for Multi-Collateral Derivatives \u003c/a>for more information.\u003c/blockquote>\u003cp>\u003c/p>\u003cblockquote>\u003cstrong>Settlement Index: \u003c/strong>The settlement rate is calculated using observations of the underlying Real Time Index over the period of 7:30 UTC to 8:00 UTC on Last Trading day. \u003cbr/>The methodology is as follows: \u003cbr/>- Take a 30 minute observation window of Real Time Index values before 8 UTC\u003cbr/>- Split the window into 1 minute partitions\u003cbr/>- Compute the average Real Time Index for each minute\u003cbr/>- Compute the average of all 1 minute partitions to obtain the Settlement Rate\u003c/blockquote>\u003cp>\u003c/p>\u003cblockquote>\u003cstrong>Settlement time: \u003c/strong>Within 15 minutes after Last Trading\u003c/blockquote>\u003cp>\u003c/p>\u003cblockquote>\u003cstrong>Last Trading: \u003c/strong>08:00 UTC \u003cbr/>\u003cbr/>Week: Every Friday\u003cbr/>\u003cbr/>Month: Last Friday of the month.\u003cbr/>\u003cbr/>Quarter: Last Friday of a month in the March quarterly cycle (March, June, September, December).\u003cbr/>\u003cbr/>Semiannual: Last Friday of a month in the March quarterly cycle (March, June, September, December).\u003c/blockquote>\u003cp>\u003c/p>\u003cblockquote>\u003cstrong>First Trading: \u003c/strong>08:00 UTC.\u003cbr/>\u003cbr/>Week: Friday of each week where no contract exists in the following week.\u003cbr/>\u003cbr/>Month: The last Friday of the calendar month where no contract exists in the following calendar month.\u003cbr/>\u003cbr/>Quarter: The last Friday of the calendar month where a contract exists in the following calendar month.\u003cbr/>\u003cbr/>Semiannual: The last Friday of the calendar month where a Month contract and Quarter contract exists.\u003cbr/>\u003cbr/>The fixed maturity listing schedule results in there always being listed simultaneously at four contracts for BTC and ETH: a Week contract, a Month contract, a Quarter contract, and a Semiannual contract. SOL only has a month and a quarter contract. No contract can have the same remaining days to maturity as another currently-listed contract, therefore at maturity, if the days remaining to maturity on one contract correspond to the maturity of a contract with fewer days to maturity, it will roll into that maturity and the new contract with more days to maturity will be listed.\u003cbr/>\u003cbr/>For example, if the monthly contract expires on the 31st of May, then the June quarterly contract will become the June monthly contract, the September quarterly contract will be listed.\u003c/blockquote>\u003cp>\u003c/p>\u003cblockquote>\u003cstrong>Initial Margin:\u003c/strong> \u003ca href=\"/articles/360022632452-Margin-Schedule\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">As low as 2%\u003c/a>\u003c/blockquote>\u003cp>\u003c/p>\u003cblockquote>\u003cstrong>Maintenance Margin: \u003c/strong>Half of Initial Margin\u003c/blockquote>\u003cp>\u003c/p>\u003cblockquote>\u003cstrong>Maximum Initial Leverage:\u003ca href=\"/articles/360022632452-Margin-Schedule\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\"> Up to 50x\u003c/a>\u003c/strong>\u003c/blockquote>\u003cp>\u003c/p>\u003cblockquote>\u003cstrong>Mark Price:\u003c/strong> Index Price plus the 30 seconds exponential moving average of the order book mid price minus the index price (future&#x27;s basis).\u003cbr/>\u003cbr/>The premium is capped at 1% for contracts with 1 day to expiry and 20% for contracts with 210 days to expiry and is linearly interpolated in between.\u003cbr/>\u003cbr/>Calculation: Index Price + EMA_30seconds(Impact Mid Price - Index Price)\u003cbr/>\u003cbr/>Note: in the extremely rare circumstance that the Index Price is unavailable for whatever reason, the above caps may not apply and the Mark Price will be equal to the Impact Mid Price.\u003c/blockquote>\u003cp>\u003c/p>\u003cp>\u003c/p>\u003cp>**Note that if the settlement rate reported by the Index provider is, for any reason, deemed to not adequately represent the underlying market, the Market Risk Committee of Kraken Derivatives reserves the right to select its own appropriate fair value settlement rate. If the index provider restates the price, Kraken Derivatives will settle to the first value published by the index provider at or after publication time.\u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][1541ac5174d6][field_heading":" Additional Information: ","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][231b3a6828cb][field_title":"Fixed Maturity Contract Specifications","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][0b07971fb8f0][field_heading":" Additional Information ","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][6b8077e60cf9][field_body":"\u003cp>The Impact Mid is the median of the average entry price market-selling x value of contracts and market-buying x value of contracts. \u003c/p>\u003cp>The contract values for Impact Mid are regularly updated. \u003c/p>\u003cp>For current contract-specific Impact Mid values see our API&#x27;s \u003ca href=\"https://futures.kraken.com/derivatives/api/v3/instruments\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">Instruments Endpoint\u003c/a>. \u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][6b8077e60cf9][field_heading":" Impact Mid Size ","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][e63dc5d9a447][field_body":"\u003cp>The maximum individual order size is $20,000,000 for all contracts and order types. A single order placed with a USD value higher than this amount will not execute. \u003c/p>","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][e63dc5d9a447][field_heading":" Global Platform Max Order Size ","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][fb2fad2a663a][field_body":"\u003cp>The decimal and thousands separators shown in this article may differ from the formats displayed on our trading platforms. Review our article on how we use \u003ca href=\"/articles/360001169543-Decimal-separators-points-vs-commas\">points and commas\u003c/a> for more information.\u003c/p>\n","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][fb2fad2a663a][field_heading":" Decimal & Thousands Separator Formatting ","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][295a203a6ebc][field_last_updated_label":"Last updated:","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][295a203a6ebc][field_title":"Linear Multi-Collateral Derivatives Contract Specifications","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][295a203a6ebc][field_tldr_title":"Key takeaways","template_navigation_disclaimer_uk][0984d42737d6][field_content":"\u003cp>Don&#39;t invest unless you&#39;re prepared to lose all the money you invest. This is a high-risk investment and you should not expect to be protected if something goes wrong. \u003ca href=\"https://www.kraken.com/legal/uk/disclaimer\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Take 2 minutes to learn more\u003c/a>.\u003c/p>\n","template_sc_search_bar][3334568c9794][field_support_ai_search_bar_background":"dynamic","template_sc_search_bar][3334568c9794][field_support_ai_search_bar_button_text":"Ask AI","template_sc_search_bar][3334568c9794][field_support_ai_search_bar_filter_all_selected_label":"All Products","template_sc_search_bar][3334568c9794][field_support_ai_search_bar_filter_by_label":"Filter by","template_sc_search_bar][3334568c9794][field_support_ai_search_bar_filter_placeholder":"Select Product","template_sc_search_bar][3334568c9794][field_support_ai_search_bar_filter_select_all_label":"Select all","template_sc_search_bar][3334568c9794][field_support_ai_search_bar_filter_selected_label":"selected","template_sc_search_bar][3334568c9794][field_support_ai_search_bar_input_placeholder":"Type your question here","template_sc_search_bar][3334568c9794][field_support_ai_search_bar_recommended_searches][0":"How do I deposit cash into my account?","template_sc_search_bar][3334568c9794][field_support_ai_search_bar_recommended_searches][1":"I need help with account verification","template_sc_search_bar][3334568c9794][field_support_ai_search_bar_recommended_searches][2":"Why can't I access my account?","template_sc_search_bar][3334568c9794][field_support_ai_search_bar_recommended_searches][3":"Are there any crypto withdrawal fees?","template_sc_search_bar][3334568c9794][field_support_ai_search_bar_recommended_searches][4":"I need help signing into my account","template_sc_search_bar_lc_layout][41525fbd006c][field_route_content_wrapper_type":"article","template_sc_search_bar_lc_layout][dd81b4434c80][field_route_content_wrapper_type":"article","template_sc_search_bar][24861306-1d6a-47e0-836e-d8ddb52e4906][field_category":"editable","template_sc_search_bar][0fdee94c3d27][description":"Force the component to be displayed in reading mode","template_sc_search_bar][8ff8eaf55b5d][description":"Set initial filters to the search bar. Only select 'Product' taxonomies. e.g. 'Product: Consumer Web'","template_sc_search_bar][74172c399795][description":"Enable to display a dialog when performing a search","template_sc_search_bar][e95331c2edb6][description":"Defaults to theme dynamic (changes based on page theme) if not provided","template_sc_need_help_widget][24e8facd1413][field_support_need_help_section_chat_card_description":"The quickest way to solve a problem is to chat with us","template_sc_need_help_widget][24e8facd1413][field_support_need_help_section_chat_card_title":"Chat with us","template_sc_need_help_widget][24e8facd1413][field_support_need_help_section_email_card_description":"Something specific? Email us and we’ll get back to you","template_sc_need_help_widget][24e8facd1413][field_support_need_help_section_email_card_title":"Email us","template_sc_need_help_widget][24e8facd1413][field_support_need_help_section_heading":"Need more help?","template_sc_need_help_widget][24e8facd1413][field_support_need_help_section_phone_card_description":"Prefer to speak over the phone? Give us a call and talk to one of our specialists","template_sc_need_help_widget][24e8facd1413][field_support_need_help_section_phone_card_title":"Call us","template_sc_need_help_widget][24e8facd1413][field_support_need_help_section_recommended_badge_text":"Recommended","template_sc_need_help_widget][24e8facd1413][field_support_need_help_section_signed_in_button_text":"Contact us","template_sc_need_help_widget][24e8facd1413][field_support_need_help_section_signed_out_button_text":"Sign in to contact us","template_sc_need_help_widget_lc_layout][42ecdc3bd208][field_route_content_wrapper_type":"article","template_sc_need_help_widget_lc_layout][e515bafe32b5][field_route_content_wrapper_type":"article","template_sc_need_help_widget][7eae3811bdcb][description":"Enable to display the contact cards: chat, phone, email","template_sc_need_help_widget][ffea5ceab77a][description":"Enable to force the cards to be displayed in tablet view for larger screens"}}}},"mode":{"cookie":null,"qs":null},"dehydratedState":{"mutations":[],"queries":[{"dehydratedAt":1784279003826,"state":{"data":{"products":[{"_createdAt":"2026-02-04T22:32:38Z","_hash":"7ed991e377d0ca29642a41411d5f4fc4db151fd96e8cad225823d45ca62ffec0d1a4488838c2939fc90651ecdd27f1f3b99eaf935da287aa32a8d52b5d860edb","_id":"2afafb32-1578-46fa-a932-d23741fdc89d","_rev":"q7LIYU0rgg5GoOCkyU1OHo","_type":"taxonomyProduct","_updatedAt":"2026-02-05T09:45:05Z","deprecated":false,"displayName":"Beholder","displayOrder":11,"editable":true,"firstPublishedAt":"2026-02-05T09:45:02.519Z","lastPublishedAt":"2026-02-05T09:45:02.519Z","name":"Product: Beholder","topArticles":[{"_key":"41a1f18255ed","reference":{"_ref":"27bd42bf-82e5-4152-814b-ec109892b611","_type":"page","_id":"27bd42bf-82e5-4152-814b-ec109892b611","_system":{"base":{"id":"27bd42bf-82e5-4152-814b-ec109892b611","rev":"SKZUWdNvIrEo0Nx0nDMpW6"}},"appId":"support","content_source_locale":"en_us","enabled_locales":[],"fiat_currency":{"_ref":"ea02af50-e496-4cad-bf6b-cb559e0ca662","_type":"taxonomyFiatCurrency","_createdAt":"2022-01-19T11:40:36Z","_hash":"964470f283fb1bc09f42172545216d2abf895ba70e247604e8a9dd6b3c8c18cab8ad659fa4e93d9fd19e769b7886bb204ef64e2c459f9a47fda61e45d6cc5988","_id":"ea02af50-e496-4cad-bf6b-cb559e0ca662","_rev":"k7u4iPUQr2vwAUdtxY2aLu","_system":{"base":{"id":"ea02af50-e496-4cad-bf6b-cb559e0ca662","rev":"1SgTMJNCZWgOJPpgh0ZIsv"}},"_updatedAt":"2025-09-19T08:12:46Z","field_apy":"4.5%","field_bonded_apy":"6.5%","field_bonded_lockup_period":"30D","field_crypto_shortcode":"USD","field_cryptowatch_id":98,"field_currencyNameFor":"for US Dollar","field_currencyNamePlural":"US Dollars","field_currencyNamePluralTo":"to US Dollars","field_currencyNameTo":"to US Dollar","field_currency_symbol":"$","field_staking_disclaimer":"\u003cp>*Eligible countries only.\u003cbr />\n\u003ca href=\"https://support.kraken.com/hc/en-us/categories/360002119091-Staking-Funds\">Learn more\u003c/a>\u003c/p>\n","field_staking_reward_cadence":"Yearly rewards","field_staking_type":"Off-chain","lastPublishedAt":"2025-09-19T08:12:43.491Z","name":"US Dollar"},"field_header_variant":"standard","field_page_components":[{"_key":"d03c0fd9693a","_type":"paragraphArticleLayout","field_article_breadcrumb_label":"Support","field_article_breadcrumbs":true,"field_audio_title":"Kraken AI podcast","field_author_additional_text":"By","field_children":[{"_key":"a7b315b5aa5f","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Beholder provides a seamless gateway to decentralized finance (DeFi), allowing you to manage, trade, and earn yield on cryptocurrencies, all while retaining complete control of your assets. Enjoy the convenience and simplicity of Kraken combined with the security and autonomy of self-custody.\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>\u003cstrong>With Beholder you get:\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"1501a0f06b28","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"dede6263bfd4","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"595f7c8452cf","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Self-custody: \u003c/strong>You retain full control of your assets with a Beholder Global Wallet, a non-custodial wallet fully owned by you. Kraken cannot access or control your private keys, ensuring maximum security and autonomy.\u003c/p>\n"}]},{"_key":"d71cb8a4d743","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"51bb617c3463","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Easy wallet creation: \u003c/strong>Quickly set up your wallet using your email, Google/Apple account, passkey, or external wallets.\u003c/p>\n"}]},{"_key":"91aa3a6169fb","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"b31d0b06985e","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>One place to do it all\u003c/strong>: Connect all of your external wallets to track your portfolios, see curated DeFi yield opportunities, and swap into any token on selected EVM networks (i.e. Ethereum, Ink, Base, Arbitrum, Optimism) or Solana.\u003c/p>\n"}]},{"_key":"33200fe39466","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"3294d1a00eb7","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Simple and intuitive interface: \u003c/strong>Perform gasless transactions, swap tokens, and earn yield easily, with all blockchain interactions happening seamlessly in the background.\u003c/p>\n"}]}],"field_type":"ul"},{"_key":"5dae342212c3","_type":"paragraphArticleHeadingBody","field_heading":"Beholder features","field_level":1,"field_skip_navigation":false},{"_key":"272f6af2e3f8","_type":"paragraphAccordion","field_children":[{"_key":"895036086a0b","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"4930f5f0e86b","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Your Beholder Global Wallet allows you to securely hold, manage, and utilize your digital assets. Once created, you can use this wallet across various decentralized applications like Uniswap or Aave, expanding your access to DeFi opportunities.\u003c/p>\n"}],"field_id":"beholder-global-wallet","field_is_expanded":false,"field_title":"Beholder Global Wallet"},{"_key":"55242fab1da4","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"de4558145095","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Funding your Beholder Global Wallet is simple and quick. Options include:\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"a2bebb5322ed","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"fd39ff73c2e1","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"91b34521bb1a","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Transfer directly from your Kraken account.\u003c/p>\n"}]},{"_key":"b34fad1cb719","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"6aa0a5c1997e","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Buy crypto instantly using a debit/credit card and Apple or Google Pay.\u003c/p>\n"}]},{"_key":"4bd8faa32188","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"993ddd59c3c9","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Receive crypto from other wallets or exchanges.\u003c/p>\n"}]}],"field_type":"ul"}],"field_id":"instant-funding-options","field_is_expanded":false,"field_title":"Instant funding options"},{"_key":"a373373330c5","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"8db8f1665fc3","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Swap tokens across multiple blockchain networks directly within Beholder without needing to hold gas tokens, manually sign, or approve transactions on-chain. Everything is managed smoothly in the background, ensuring a user-friendly experience similar to centralized exchanges.\u003c/p>\n"}],"field_id":"effortless-swaps","field_is_expanded":false,"field_title":"Effortless swaps"},{"_key":"21c6ca8a4746","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"35612ba7fc64","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Deposit your assets into a wide variety of vaults and start earning yield immediately. Beholder also offers curated yield-generating strategies from trusted DeFi partners.\u003c/p>\n"}],"field_id":"earn-yield","field_is_expanded":false,"field_title":"Earn yield"},{"_key":"4f6aaf90e937","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"a71e7de5cd0a","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Beholder supports multiple blockchain networks, such as Ethereum, Ink, Base, Arbitrum, Optimism, and Solana. Easily explore trending tokens, popular assets, and innovative DeFi opportunities across various chains directly from the homepage.\u003c/p>\n"}],"field_id":"supported-networks","field_is_expanded":false,"field_title":"Supported networks"},{"_key":"0d2bf3597505","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"42a41a191b0d","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Beholder prioritizes your security and privacy:\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"5cb8551589b4","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"49e8ead340eb","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"3f40464c2ea6","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Kraken does not control or store your private keys.\u003c/p>\n"}]},{"_key":"b5f4bc7385f5","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"455eacf45914","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>All keys are securely embedded within the application, ensuring only you have access.\u003c/p>\n"}]},{"_key":"872a1aa058ae","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"30aebe28df33","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Your Beholder Global Wallet remains exclusively yours and can be freely used across the broader decentralized ecosystem.\u003c/p>\n"}]}],"field_type":"ul"}],"field_id":"security-and-privacy","field_is_expanded":false,"field_title":"Security and privacy"},{"_key":"40d4f7806a30","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"332b42f56a10","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Beholder is open to everyone, \u003cstrong>not just existing Kraken clients.\u003c/strong> Create a wallet and get started immediately, no Kraken account necessary.\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>&nbsp;\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Please note:\u003c/strong> Beholder is not available for residents of Canada, Australia, and the United Kingdom.\u003c/p>\n"}],"field_id":"open-to-everyone","field_is_expanded":false,"field_title":"Open to everyone"}],"field_emit_faq_schema":false},{"_key":"d327451f0f56","_type":"paragraphArticleHeadingBody","field_heading":"Ready to get started?","field_level":2,"field_skip_navigation":false},{"_key":"5c9f25f50221","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"697684258921","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"a417ef393952","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003ca href=\"https://support.kraken.com/articles/create-manage-beholder-account\" target=\"_blank\">How to create or manage your Beholder account\u003c/a>\u003c/p>\n"}]},{"_key":"dd439ca6f100","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"8bb829b375e6","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003ca href=\"https://support.kraken.com/articles/fund-beholder\" target=\"_blank\">How to fund your Beholder account\u003c/a>\u003c/p>\n"}]}],"field_type":"ul"}],"field_last_updated_label":"Last updated:","field_read_time_additional_text":"min","field_subtitle_type":"heading5","field_title":"What is Beholder?","field_title_type":"heading1","field_tldr_title":"Key takeaways"}],"field_sitemap_definition":{"field_sitemap_disable":false,"field_sitemap_external_data":{"equities_params":{"page":1,"page_size":10,"sort_order":"descending"},"futures_instruments_params":{"endpointType":"FUTURES_INSTRUMENTS_SUBSCRIBER"},"params":{"position":0}}},"firstPublishedAt":"2026-02-04T21:23:52.292Z","lastPublishedAt":"2026-02-05T21:12:01.062Z","locale":{"_ref":"6a947fc0-ff5d-4972-a190-1bde98fa51a3","_type":"taxonomyLocales","_id":"6a947fc0-ff5d-4972-a190-1bde98fa51a3","code":"en-us","field_label":"English","name":"en-US"},"owners":["peokEqxGP"],"path":"/articles/what-is-beholder","status":true,"title":"What is Beholder?"}},{"_key":"622ed003a2ef","reference":{"_ref":"de861e35-b633-4c29-9e34-bee0df082d21","_type":"page","_id":"de861e35-b633-4c29-9e34-bee0df082d21","_system":{"base":{"id":"de861e35-b633-4c29-9e34-bee0df082d21","rev":"J1gDhhHcojGlsOMy0Ng21j"}},"appId":"support","content_source_locale":"en_us","enabled_locales":[],"fiat_currency":{"_ref":"ea02af50-e496-4cad-bf6b-cb559e0ca662","_type":"taxonomyFiatCurrency","_createdAt":"2022-01-19T11:40:36Z","_hash":"964470f283fb1bc09f42172545216d2abf895ba70e247604e8a9dd6b3c8c18cab8ad659fa4e93d9fd19e769b7886bb204ef64e2c459f9a47fda61e45d6cc5988","_id":"ea02af50-e496-4cad-bf6b-cb559e0ca662","_rev":"k7u4iPUQr2vwAUdtxY2aLu","_system":{"base":{"id":"ea02af50-e496-4cad-bf6b-cb559e0ca662","rev":"1SgTMJNCZWgOJPpgh0ZIsv"}},"_updatedAt":"2025-09-19T08:12:46Z","field_apy":"4.5%","field_bonded_apy":"6.5%","field_bonded_lockup_period":"30D","field_crypto_shortcode":"USD","field_cryptowatch_id":98,"field_currencyNameFor":"for US Dollar","field_currencyNamePlural":"US Dollars","field_currencyNamePluralTo":"to US Dollars","field_currencyNameTo":"to US Dollar","field_currency_symbol":"$","field_staking_disclaimer":"\u003cp>*Eligible countries only.\u003cbr />\n\u003ca href=\"https://support.kraken.com/hc/en-us/categories/360002119091-Staking-Funds\">Learn more\u003c/a>\u003c/p>\n","field_staking_reward_cadence":"Yearly rewards","field_staking_type":"Off-chain","lastPublishedAt":"2025-09-19T08:12:43.491Z","name":"US Dollar"},"field_header_variant":"standard","field_page_components":[{"_key":"a901a996e475","_type":"paragraphArticleLayout","field_article_breadcrumb_label":"Support","field_article_breadcrumbs":true,"field_audio_title":"Kraken AI podcast","field_author_additional_text":"By","field_children":[{"_key":"60c3fb3e12f2","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Beholder allows you to securely manage your cryptocurrencies using a self-custodial wallet integrated seamlessly into Kraken.com. This article guides you step-by-step through creating and managing your account.\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"25dd969e9d7a","_type":"paragraphAccordion","field_children":[{"_key":"5b7579133293","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"7dc1acfcf503","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"80fb9768eac0","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"e5cb38b39b80","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>First, go to \u003ca href=\"https://beholder.kraken.com\" style=\"text-decoration:none\">\u003cu>beholder.kraken.com\u003c/u>\u003c/a>.\u003c/p>\n"}]},{"_key":"0aad9a6781cd","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"6fef92b1c5f7","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Click the \u003cstrong>Connect\u003c/strong> button in the top right of the Discover page\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"30bb4b3fc2e2","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_align":"left","field_image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-67a828387e9a556c474a6dd43d9793474f964ba9-106x53-jpg","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/jpeg","originalFilename":"pasted-image.jpg","size":3383,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":2,"height":53,"width":106},"lqip":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"_id":"image-67a828387e9a556c474a6dd43d9793474f964ba9-106x53-jpg","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/67a828387e9a556c474a6dd43d9793474f964ba9-106x53.jpg"}},"field_width":"25"}]},{"_key":"edfd14bde574","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"94fbb45a8852","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Select your preferred method for creating a Beholder account. These methods include email, passkey, an existing wallet (like MetaMask or Phantom), or Google/Apple accounts.\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"43721e32c70a","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_align":"left","field_image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-e72fa781f7ea3645cb970a1cf12287af085fea4f-686x1172-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"image.png","size":77786,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":0.5853242320819113,"height":1172,"width":686},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-e72fa781f7ea3645cb970a1cf12287af085fea4f-686x1172-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/e72fa781f7ea3645cb970a1cf12287af085fea4f-686x1172.png"}},"field_width":"48"},{"_key":"ad33bbc67262","_type":"paragraphNotification","field_can_be_closed":false,"field_closed_state_is_persistent":true,"field_direction":"stacked","field_has_icon":false,"field_text":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Note: \u003c/strong>If you choose to create your Beholder account using an existing wallet, you&rsquo;ll need to connect this wallet to Beholder. \u003cstrong>\u003cem>If you connect an external wallet to Beholder, make sure you have the private keys of that wallet backed up, and add a passkey to your account. If you lose access to the wallet that created your Beholder account, you&rsquo;ll lose access to funds on Beholder. \u003c/em>\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>\n","field_tone":"negative"}]},{"_key":"7ddfc1d6f7e6","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"fb33bcded773","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>That&rsquo;s it! Your Beholder account is ready to be funded. Your wallet addresses have been generated, and can be viewed and copied by clicking the \u003cstrong>Profile\u003c/strong> icon in the top right corner.\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"30308885749d","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_align":"left","field_image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-36c04623e9011bd6c33cb69f3492530554daa013-678x984-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"Screenshot 2026-02-04 at 00.01.11.png","size":76096,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":0.6890243902439024,"height":984,"width":678},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-36c04623e9011bd6c33cb69f3492530554daa013-678x984-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/36c04623e9011bd6c33cb69f3492530554daa013-678x984.png"}},"field_width":"48"}]}],"field_type":"ol"}],"field_id":"creating-your-beholder-account","field_is_expanded":false,"field_title":"Creating your Beholder account"}],"field_emit_faq_schema":false},{"_key":"8d6efc327daf","_type":"paragraphArticleHeadingBody","field_body":"\u003cp>After creating your Beholder account, you can connect your Kraken account, add more wallets, and tweak additional account settings. These functions can be accessed by clicking the \u003cstrong>Wallet\u003c/strong> icon(s) in the top right corner.\u003c/p>\n","field_heading":"How to manage your Beholder account","field_level":1,"field_skip_navigation":false},{"_key":"f270897143d6","_type":"paragraphAccordion","field_children":[{"_key":"b5455da49d39","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"24c84cc92ff4","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Connecting your Kraken account is fast and simple. When you connect your Kraken account to your Beholder account, this allows you to seamlessly transfer funds between the accounts. To connect your Kraken account, follow the steps below:\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"966fef6ccc35","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"433b2589c98c","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"aadeb41914d7","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Click the \u003cstrong>Profile\u003c/strong> icon in the top right corner of the page, and then click \u003cstrong>Connect your Kraken account\u003c/strong>.\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"778e101ce612","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_align":"left","field_image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-dc3065da891bb216d882791d31950b9f4c0cb18e-339x475-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"Screenshot 2026-02-03 at 11.22.26.png","size":32197,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":0.7136842105263158,"height":475,"width":339},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-dc3065da891bb216d882791d31950b9f4c0cb18e-339x475-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/dc3065da891bb216d882791d31950b9f4c0cb18e-339x475.png"}},"field_width":"48"}]},{"_key":"cc896b490448","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"60d222b970bd","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>You&rsquo;ll then be taken to the Kraken Sign In page, sign into your Kraken account. After entering your sign-in details, you may be required to confirm via email.&nbsp;\u003c/p>\n"}]},{"_key":"bf184e917b58","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"2584df09c831","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>After signing into your Kraken account, you&rsquo;ll be automatically taken back to Beholder with your account now successfully connected.\u003c/p>\n"}]}],"field_type":"ol"}],"field_id":"connecting-your-kraken-account","field_is_expanded":false,"field_title":"Connecting your Kraken account"},{"_key":"cd3e84a54d46","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"022a6b4a7c35","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>External wallets, such as Metamask and Phantom, can be added to your Beholder account. This will allow you to transact and view assets within these wallets. Please keep in mind, transactions in Beholder initiated from your external wallet are not gasless and you will be prompted to sign transactions from your external wallet. To add an external wallet, follow these instructions:\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"6a679e88d04a","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"264c1822aa87","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"3e73a63cf888","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Click the \u003cstrong>Wallet\u003c/strong> icon(s) in the top-right corner of the page, then click&nbsp;\u003cstrong>Add.\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"9de14cef438d","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_align":"left","field_image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-a1d75c74421a707b98dba5261a069757bb44ddf8-678x526-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"Screenshot 2026-02-04 at 00.21.30.png","size":41976,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":1.2889733840304183,"height":526,"width":678},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-a1d75c74421a707b98dba5261a069757bb44ddf8-678x526-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/a1d75c74421a707b98dba5261a069757bb44ddf8-678x526.png"}},"field_width":"48"}]},{"_key":"077db7a187fd","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"5c7ec1743812","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>You can now&nbsp;\u003cstrong>Connect a wallet\u003c/strong>&nbsp;or&nbsp;\u003cstrong>Watch a wallet\u003c/strong>.\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>If you&#39;d like to \u003cem>watch\u003c/em> a wallet, simply select that option, then enter the address/domain and give the wallet a name (optional).\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>If you&#39;d like to&nbsp;\u003cem>connect\u003c/em>&nbsp;a wallet, continue to the next step.\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"0090197b9a1e","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_align":"left","field_image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-595203026147a460fc6756b25e687fad7533bb02-692x528-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"Screenshot 2026-02-04 at 00.26.54.png","size":56956,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":1.3106060606060606,"height":528,"width":692},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-595203026147a460fc6756b25e687fad7533bb02-692x528-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/595203026147a460fc6756b25e687fad7533bb02-692x528.png"}},"field_width":"48"}]},{"_key":"1615bc722c0d","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"0627ce6882ae","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>If you elect to connect a wallet, select that option, and then choose your wallet provider.\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>\u003cstrong>The connection process may differ depending on the wallet you connect. For these instructions we will cover adding MetaMask.\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"58e78cfe73ea","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_align":"left","field_image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-35d5c7fafa4def33dd53d32d836b594907dd13ab-692x1196-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"Screenshot 2026-02-04 at 00.31.37.png","size":116345,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":0.5785953177257525,"height":1196,"width":692},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-35d5c7fafa4def33dd53d32d836b594907dd13ab-692x1196-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/35d5c7fafa4def33dd53d32d836b594907dd13ab-692x1196.png"}},"field_width":"48"},{"_key":"ea5b149794d3","_type":"paragraphNotification","field_can_be_closed":false,"field_closed_state_is_persistent":true,"field_direction":"stacked","field_has_icon":false,"field_text":"\u003cp>From this point forward, these instructions are \u003cstrong>tailored for MetaMask connections.\u003c/strong>&nbsp;Your experience may vary depending on the wallet provider you connect. If you have any questions, please reach out to \u003ca href=\"https://support.kraken.com/contact\" target=\"_blank\">Kraken Support.\u003c/a>\u003c/p>\n","field_title":"NOTICE:","field_tone":"negative"}]},{"_key":"5476bde7282b","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"ee0b138cb14b","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>If prompted, select the network the wallet account is on. In this case, Ethereum (including EVM chains) and Solana are available, and we will select the Ethereum option.\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"3aacda101927","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_align":"left","field_image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-1ee1b497223bcc20888f0e29b770bc1debcef5ec-352x342-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"image.png","size":43524,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":1.0292397660818713,"height":342,"width":352},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-1ee1b497223bcc20888f0e29b770bc1debcef5ec-352x342-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/1ee1b497223bcc20888f0e29b770bc1debcef5ec-352x342.png"}},"field_width":"48"}]},{"_key":"214f030b88a3","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"fc33d27397a8","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Next, a list of available wallet accounts on the network you selected will be presented. If this is the correct account(s), click\u003cstrong> Connect.\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"6b5311061f64","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_align":"left","field_image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-70b5216c1e7f680920585ae1dcceb2a2989806e3-391x610-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"image.png","size":81454,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":0.6409836065573771,"height":610,"width":391},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-70b5216c1e7f680920585ae1dcceb2a2989806e3-391x610-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/70b5216c1e7f680920585ae1dcceb2a2989806e3-391x610.png"}},"field_width":"48"},{"_key":"58ce9eaa53e2","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Note:&nbsp;\u003c/strong>This page may look slightly different for you (account names, quantity of accounts), in our example, we are using a hardware wallet connected through MetaMask.\u003c/p>\n"}]},{"_key":"f6f40b3e65cb","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"8db8d66f6f01","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Lastly, you&#39;ll be requested to confirm the connection. If everything looks correct, click&nbsp;\u003cstrong>Confirm.\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>If you are using a hardware wallet, like we are in this example, you will be required to sign the confirming transaction from the device.\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"636cb0d75fc9","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_align":"left","field_image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-08da90dd5833e4136a3ac8100893dacab1ce695a-391x610-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"image.png","size":157908,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":0.6409836065573771,"height":610,"width":391},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-08da90dd5833e4136a3ac8100893dacab1ce695a-391x610-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/08da90dd5833e4136a3ac8100893dacab1ce695a-391x610.png"}},"field_width":"48"},{"_key":"c97756dfffef","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Note:&nbsp;\u003c/strong>The network does not need to show &quot;Ethereum&quot; (as shown in the image). As long as it is an EVM chain (Ethereum, Polygon, Ink, Base, OP Mainnet, Arbitrum) it will properly connect to Beholder.\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>Ensure the&nbsp;\u003cstrong>Request from\u003c/strong> entry says &quot;beholder.kraken.com&quot;.\u003c/p>\n"}]}],"field_type":"ol"}],"field_id":"adding-an-external-wallet","field_is_expanded":false,"field_title":"Adding an external wallet"},{"_key":"08e36091ddb6","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"13f9117eb7ba","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>To adjust account settings, such as 2FA, backups, and connections, follow these steps:\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"552277f71beb","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"0757836a4339","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"b46a7a4318f9","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Click the \u003cstrong>Wallet\u003c/strong>&nbsp;icon(s) in the top-right corner of the page, then click&nbsp;\u003cstrong>Settings.\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"3c6cc8e88272","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_align":"left","field_image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-b8e1652aceea748a0b3724244002d43075a6c181-672x990-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"Screenshot 2026-02-04 at 01.00.34.png","size":78452,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":0.6787878787878788,"height":990,"width":672},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-b8e1652aceea748a0b3724244002d43075a6c181-672x990-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/b8e1652aceea748a0b3724244002d43075a6c181-672x990.png"}},"field_width":"48"}]},{"_key":"957f5a627603","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"9d639f9201ca","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>On the Settings page, you can adjust your sign in methods, account connections, passkey &amp; 2FA, and view/export your private key.\u003c/p>\n"}]}],"field_type":"ol"}],"field_id":"account-settings","field_is_expanded":false,"field_title":"Account settings"},{"_key":"994b0766a257","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"fb8ae47d98b0","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Beholder provides complete self-custody of your crypto assets, meaning only you have control over your wallet&rsquo;s private keys. Kraken does not and cannot access or control your funds. \u003cstrong>Beholder uses advanced key management and recovery methods, but you should still keep a secure backup of your private keys and make sure you have multiple login methods available by setting up a passkey and 2FA.&nbsp;\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>Gas fees for transactions are simplified on Beholder. The platform automatically handles gas payments and includes the cost transparently in each transaction. You don&rsquo;t need to manage or hold gas tokens separately.\u003c/p>\n"}],"field_id":"important-security-information","field_is_expanded":false,"field_title":"Important security information"}],"field_emit_faq_schema":false}],"field_last_updated_label":"Last updated:","field_read_time_additional_text":"min","field_subtitle_type":"heading5","field_title":"How to create and manage your Beholder account","field_title_type":"heading1","field_tldr_title":"Key takeaways"}],"field_sitemap_definition":{"field_sitemap_disable":false,"field_sitemap_external_data":{"equities_params":{"page":1,"page_size":10,"sort_order":"descending"},"futures_instruments_params":{"endpointType":"FUTURES_INSTRUMENTS_SUBSCRIBER"},"params":{"position":0}}},"firstPublishedAt":"2026-02-04T19:37:32.192Z","is_article":true,"lastPublishedAt":"2026-05-18T07:02:40.555Z","locale":{"_ref":"6a947fc0-ff5d-4972-a190-1bde98fa51a3","_type":"taxonomyLocales","_id":"6a947fc0-ff5d-4972-a190-1bde98fa51a3","code":"en-us","field_label":"English","name":"en-US"},"owners":["peokEqxGP"],"path":"/articles/create-manage-beholder-account","status":true,"title":"How to create and manage your Beholder account"}},{"_key":"e87cd1149ad1","reference":{"_ref":"73df9cac-3e7d-49c3-bd89-85ab1bf8487c","_type":"page","_id":"73df9cac-3e7d-49c3-bd89-85ab1bf8487c","appId":"support","content_source_locale":"en_us","enabled_locales":[],"fiat_currency":{"_ref":"ea02af50-e496-4cad-bf6b-cb559e0ca662","_type":"taxonomyFiatCurrency","_createdAt":"2022-01-19T11:40:36Z","_hash":"964470f283fb1bc09f42172545216d2abf895ba70e247604e8a9dd6b3c8c18cab8ad659fa4e93d9fd19e769b7886bb204ef64e2c459f9a47fda61e45d6cc5988","_id":"ea02af50-e496-4cad-bf6b-cb559e0ca662","_rev":"k7u4iPUQr2vwAUdtxY2aLu","_system":{"base":{"id":"ea02af50-e496-4cad-bf6b-cb559e0ca662","rev":"1SgTMJNCZWgOJPpgh0ZIsv"}},"_updatedAt":"2025-09-19T08:12:46Z","field_apy":"4.5%","field_bonded_apy":"6.5%","field_bonded_lockup_period":"30D","field_crypto_shortcode":"USD","field_cryptowatch_id":98,"field_currencyNameFor":"for US Dollar","field_currencyNamePlural":"US Dollars","field_currencyNamePluralTo":"to US Dollars","field_currencyNameTo":"to US Dollar","field_currency_symbol":"$","field_staking_disclaimer":"\u003cp>*Eligible countries only.\u003cbr />\n\u003ca href=\"https://support.kraken.com/hc/en-us/categories/360002119091-Staking-Funds\">Learn more\u003c/a>\u003c/p>\n","field_staking_reward_cadence":"Yearly rewards","field_staking_type":"Off-chain","lastPublishedAt":"2025-09-19T08:12:43.491Z","name":"US Dollar"},"field_header_variant":"standard","field_page_components":[{"_key":"c9778696a1f9","_type":"paragraphArticleLayout","field_article_breadcrumb_label":"Support","field_article_breadcrumbs":true,"field_audio_title":"Kraken AI podcast","field_author_additional_text":"By","field_children":[{"_key":"1742338015a1","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Beholder allows you to trade crypto instantly, from virtually every page. On the control panel to your right, you&rsquo;ll notice a \u003cstrong>Swap\u003c/strong> button. Using the \u003cstrong>Swap\u003c/strong> button, you can easily swap from one cryptocurrency to another, \u003cstrong>across chains.\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"78e29643efad","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_align":"center","field_image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-0d87aa2ad152f4b3be533ba4ef11b8b51bc0e6b5-1134x1600-jpg","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/jpeg","originalFilename":"pasted-image.jpg","size":202529,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":0.70875,"height":1600,"width":1134},"lqip":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"_id":"image-0d87aa2ad152f4b3be533ba4ef11b8b51bc0e6b5-1134x1600-jpg","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/0d87aa2ad152f4b3be533ba4ef11b8b51bc0e6b5-1134x1600.jpg"}},"field_width":"48"},{"_key":"b9c700b48d9f","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Swapping across chains means you can swap USDT0 that you have on the Ethereum Network, into USDC on the Ink Network, or directly into a SOL coin that you like. Beholder handles all the intermediate steps for you with a single click. Swaps can be executed via the control panel, as well as from an asset page containing a price chart.\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"788397322658","_type":"paragraphAccordion","field_children":[{"_key":"bd6f7b925624","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"9ab62c6266a3","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Swapping crypto from the control panel is the quickest way to execute your swap. From all of the main screens, the control panel is available on your right hand side. To swap crypto using the control panel, follow these instructions:\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"c6108854f953","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"b8731e477300","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"270e506f2aa0","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Click \u003cstrong>Swap\u003c/strong> in the control panel.\u003c/p>\n"}]},{"_key":"3faec19acaca","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"820a649574db","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Click the \u003cstrong>Token\u003c/strong> dropdown in the \u003cstrong>From\u003c/strong> section. Here is where you select the token you&rsquo;d like to swap into another token. Here you can search for specific tokens, connected wallets, sort by network, or you can view all of your tokens across all networks.\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"6d906be5924f","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_align":"left","field_image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-33912563dc18409c2bb69c3f989e78200c450974-660x890-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"Screenshot 2026-02-04 at 02.34.23.png","size":65636,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":0.7415730337078652,"height":890,"width":660},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-33912563dc18409c2bb69c3f989e78200c450974-660x890-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/33912563dc18409c2bb69c3f989e78200c450974-660x890.png"}},"field_width":"48"}]},{"_key":"0c9ec44e5bc2","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"2e0c8890b1ec","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>After you&rsquo;ve selected the token, enter the amount of this token you&rsquo;d like to swap. You can enter this in the selected token (e.g. 0.005 ETH), or you can enter the amount in USD (e.g. $10). You can swap between entry methods by clicking the double arrows by the price.\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"6c799d631100","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_align":"left","field_image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-a41dae21adb8a1ad65ad87c59071824cfa1f0fb3-660x940-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"Screenshot 2026-02-04 at 02.37.30.png","size":87955,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":0.7021276595744681,"height":940,"width":660},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-a41dae21adb8a1ad65ad87c59071824cfa1f0fb3-660x940-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/a41dae21adb8a1ad65ad87c59071824cfa1f0fb3-660x940.png"}},"field_width":"48"}]},{"_key":"725131a3967d","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"9ad45a301250","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Then, select the token you&rsquo;d like to receive. You can do this by clicking the\u003cstrong>&nbsp;Token dropdown\u003c/strong>&nbsp;button in the \u003cstrong>To\u003c/strong> section.\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp>This will open the token finder, where you can select any token from any eligible chain. You may search for a token, choose a token you already own, or look through trending tokens.\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"707c3838b0aa","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_align":"left","field_image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-72cf50869a99f49b456ebab47f272c0bf358d505-660x940-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"Screenshot 2026-02-04 at 02.39.48.png","size":88064,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":0.7021276595744681,"height":940,"width":660},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-72cf50869a99f49b456ebab47f272c0bf358d505-660x940-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/72cf50869a99f49b456ebab47f272c0bf358d505-660x940.png"}},"field_width":"48"}]},{"_key":"55715a0177fa","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"3594a96ae225","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>The amount of your \u003cstrong>To \u003c/strong>token will automatically populate based on the amount you&rsquo;re spending of the \u003cstrong>From\u003c/strong> token. You can adjust both sides of the form, and the other side will always automatically update.\u003c/p>\n"}]},{"_key":"100b6be7d45c","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"d72d10abffd5","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Review the transaction information, including the conversion rate and estimated gas fee at the bottom of the Swap form. Then, click \u003cstrong>Swap now.\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"3d4bda3d06ce","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_align":"left","field_image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-0de66a7980579ca42d409fc9161c821ee8e76209-660x948-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"Screenshot 2026-02-04 at 02.41.25.png","size":88402,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":0.6962025316455697,"height":948,"width":660},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-0de66a7980579ca42d409fc9161c821ee8e76209-660x948-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/0de66a7980579ca42d409fc9161c821ee8e76209-660x948.png"}},"field_width":"48"}]}],"field_type":"ol"}],"field_id":"swap-using-the-control-panel","field_is_expanded":false,"field_title":"Swap using the control panel"},{"_key":"57c70c4388c2","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"797da817da1e","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>If you&rsquo;d like to view the chart or explore trending tokens, we&rsquo;ve got you covered. At any time if you click an asset, whether it&rsquo;s in the trending list, from the \u003ca href=\"https://beholder.kraken.com/trade?tokensTab=trending&amp;tokensInterval=1h\" target=\"_blank\">Trade page\u003c/a>, in your wallet, or in search results, it will bring you to that tokens asset page. To view the chart for the token you&rsquo;re swapping to, follow these steps:\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"744346e983b5","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"25799719ad70","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"cc7141282879","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Search for the token you&rsquo;d like to swap to, and would like to view the chart for. The \u003cstrong>search bar is located at the top of each page\u003c/strong> in Beholder.\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"bef1b321fad5","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_align":"left","field_image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-fbfe08c0cb79775f923cfb9c1ad2ac1ada3d4cfb-409x52-jpg","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/jpeg","originalFilename":"pasted-image.jpg","size":4420,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":7.865384615384615,"height":52,"width":409},"lqip":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"_id":"image-fbfe08c0cb79775f923cfb9c1ad2ac1ada3d4cfb-409x52-jpg","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/fbfe08c0cb79775f923cfb9c1ad2ac1ada3d4cfb-409x52.jpg"}},"field_width":"100"}]},{"_key":"fa22e359f380","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"540f12a25010","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Once you click the Search bar, you can manually type in the name of a token, paste the contract address of a token, or explore our curated list of assets.\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"da04c41019fa","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_align":"left","field_image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-013dd971aa4beb5b8d75b781c20b8f2055c802cd-2228x1364-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"Screenshot 2026-02-04 at 02.47.01.png","size":438922,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":1.6334310850439884,"height":1364,"width":2228},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-013dd971aa4beb5b8d75b781c20b8f2055c802cd-2228x1364-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/013dd971aa4beb5b8d75b781c20b8f2055c802cd-2228x1364.png"}},"field_width":"100"}]},{"_key":"ea4874e49df6","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"168792ca9f39","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>After finding the token you&rsquo;d like to \u003cstrong>swap to,\u003c/strong> click on it to open the asset page. A Swap form will also automatically input this token in the \u003cstrong>To \u003c/strong>section of the form.\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"aed3cd7259bd","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_align":"left","field_image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-451c1d677c3de514208f297fe6c4eceefa054f97-1600x695-jpg","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/jpeg","originalFilename":"pasted-image.jpg","size":284759,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":2.302158273381295,"height":695,"width":1600},"lqip":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"_id":"image-451c1d677c3de514208f297fe6c4eceefa054f97-1600x695-jpg","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/451c1d677c3de514208f297fe6c4eceefa054f97-1600x695.jpg"}},"field_width":"100"}]},{"_key":"ff9c804c7d88","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"faf61ba4719d","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Click the\u003cstrong>&nbsp;token\u003c/strong> \u003cstrong>dropdown\u003c/strong> in the \u003cstrong>From\u003c/strong> section. Here is where you select the token you&rsquo;d like to swap away. You can sort by network, or you can view all of your assets across all networks.\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"423828961e16","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_align":"left","field_image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-2dab62a3b4664439813ce0c00b9e2c61928112b4-668x948-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"Screenshot 2026-02-04 at 02.49.20.png","size":91324,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":0.7046413502109705,"height":948,"width":668},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-2dab62a3b4664439813ce0c00b9e2c61928112b4-668x948-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/2dab62a3b4664439813ce0c00b9e2c61928112b4-668x948.png"}},"field_width":"48"},{"_key":"04808a8cb72f","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>After you&rsquo;ve selected the token, enter the amount of this token you&rsquo;d like to swap.\u003c/p>\n"}]},{"_key":"f14fc720fa1d","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"63cd0dcbde6d","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>The amount of your \u003cstrong>To \u003c/strong>token will automatically populate based on the amount you&rsquo;re spending of the \u003cstrong>From\u003c/strong> token. You can adjust both sides of the form, and the other side will always automatically update.\u003c/p>\n"}]},{"_key":"d074a67d628d","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"a0c202690287","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Review the transaction information, including the conversion rate and estimated gas fee at the bottom of the Swap form. Then, click \u003cstrong>Swap now.\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"53665d87fd4a","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_align":"left","field_image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-1db6bcd6a2811aa9a7295c438c69c8cd16b3e135-668x948-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"Screenshot 2026-02-04 at 02.51.31.png","size":92730,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":0.7046413502109705,"height":948,"width":668},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-1db6bcd6a2811aa9a7295c438c69c8cd16b3e135-668x948-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/1db6bcd6a2811aa9a7295c438c69c8cd16b3e135-668x948.png"}},"field_width":"48"}]}],"field_type":"ol"}],"field_id":"swap-while-viewing-a-chart","field_is_expanded":false,"field_title":"Swap while viewing a chart"}],"field_emit_faq_schema":false}],"field_last_updated_label":"Last updated:","field_read_time_additional_text":"min","field_subtitle_type":"heading5","field_title":"How to swap crypto on Beholder","field_title_type":"heading1","field_tldr_title":"Key takeaways"}],"field_sitemap_definition":{"field_sitemap_disable":false,"field_sitemap_external_data":{"equities_params":{"page":1,"page_size":10,"sort_order":"descending"},"futures_instruments_params":{"endpointType":"FUTURES_INSTRUMENTS_SUBSCRIBER"},"params":{"position":0}}},"firstPublishedAt":"2026-02-04T20:24:55.249Z","lastPublishedAt":"2026-02-04T20:24:55.249Z","locale":{"_ref":"6a947fc0-ff5d-4972-a190-1bde98fa51a3","_type":"taxonomyLocales","_id":"6a947fc0-ff5d-4972-a190-1bde98fa51a3","code":"en-us","field_label":"English","name":"en-US"},"owners":["peokEqxGP"],"path":"/articles/swap-beholder","status":true,"title":"How to swap crypto on Beholder"}}],"visibility":[{"_key":"d739e25cab77","component":"searchFilter","value":true}]},{"_createdAt":"2025-03-06T16:06:26Z","_id":"43d8f5f3-50ec-42b7-8bac-db2bbfb8afd9","_key":"245cc02c6ae7","_rev":"R4bDO5qNaIcYVJNTEZsDyn","_type":"taxonomyProduct","_updatedAt":"2025-05-30T08:07:28Z","deprecated":false,"description":"REST, WebSocket, and FIX APIs","displayName":"API","editable":true,"name":"Product: API","topArticles":[{"_key":"e1ba2a585a19","reference":{"_ref":"article-360000672023","_type":"page","_id":"article-360000672023","appId":"support","content_source_locale":"en_us","enabled_locales":[],"field_page_components":[{"_key":"f7cb0a29db36","_type":"paragraphArticleLayout","field_article_breadcrumb_label":"Support","field_article_breadcrumbs":true,"field_children":[{"_key":"c3c3b491247e","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cblockquote>API is an acronym for Application Programming Interface.\u003c/blockquote>\u003cp>In general, an API is an interface that allows two unrelated systems to interact with each other (in the same sense that a restaurant server enables the customer and the chef to interact). An API specification describes the way that each of the two systems must interact with the API itself (such as the language that must be used, the syntax of messages that are passed back and forth, how quickly messages can be sent, etc.).\u003c/p>\u003cp>Specifically for cryptocurrency trading, our APIs enables you to interact with our exchanges programmatically (via software instead of a human interface), allowing you to obtain real time market data, make trades and manage your account.\u003c/p>\u003cp>A few of the tasks that can be accomplished via our API:\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"8a1c5f9c3607","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"1eaad94fbf85","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"3af28767b396","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Download historical market data\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"9660abf8babf","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"6813662e5af2","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Stream real time market data\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"5b2344e07c39","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"8c61fe4526cf","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Place and cancel trading orders\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"9cc74b975f5a","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"16309d022e4f","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>View account balances, download trading history, make funding transactions\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"9eec5fbb0b11","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"3086a898eb5c","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Allocate or deallocate funds to an earn strategy\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"2f731ffafcea","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"db75016a5c0e","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>and much more ...\u003c/p>"}]}],"field_type":"ul"},{"_key":"5233dd7f7583","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Our API developer center provides detailed specifications and instructions for using our REST API, WebSocket API, and FIX API; and our \u003ca href=\"/sections/360004645712-API-Basics\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">API Support articles \u003c/a>provide additional information about specific tasks (such as how to retrieve our historical market data) along with a variety of example code and in depth explanations.\u003c/p>\u003cp>We also provide support and additional services for institutions that wish to integrate with our APIs. Please contact us directly via the\u003ca href=\"/forms/360000104043\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\"> support form here\u003c/a> for more information.\u003c/p>"}],"field_last_updated_label":"Last updated:","field_title":"What is an API? What does an API do?","field_tldr_title":"Key takeaways"}],"field_page_meta":{"description":"Support Center for Kraken.com | Bitcoin & Cryptocurrency Exchange | Bitcoin Trading Platform","title":"What is an API? What does an API do? | Kraken"},"field_tags":[{"_key":"d31b3d8cd9bc","_ref":"0101da93-4985-4fab-b89e-d48a52587d13","_type":"taxonomyTag","_id":"0101da93-4985-4fab-b89e-d48a52587d13","firstPublishedAt":"2026-01-20T10:38:41.280Z","lastPublishedAt":"2026-01-20T10:38:41.280Z","name":"sc-tier-4"}],"locale":{"_ref":"6a947fc0-ff5d-4972-a190-1bde98fa51a3","_type":"taxonomyLocales","_id":"6a947fc0-ff5d-4972-a190-1bde98fa51a3","code":"en-us","field_label":"English","name":"en-US"},"path":"/articles/360000672023-what-is-an-api-what-does-an-api-do-","status":true,"title":"What is an API? What does an API do?"}}],"visibility":[{"_key":"ca7e7e8ac2f1","component":"searchFilter","value":true}]},{"_createdAt":"2025-03-06T16:06:26Z","_id":"product-Futures","_key":"bd2d4e7894f3","_rev":"R4bDO5qNaIcYVJNTEZsDyn","_type":"taxonomyProduct","_updatedAt":"2025-05-30T08:07:28Z","deprecated":false,"description":"","displayName":"Derivatives","editable":false,"name":"Product: Futures","topArticles":[],"visibility":[{"_key":"c123e21b5af1","component":"searchFilter","value":true}]},{"_createdAt":"2025-04-28T11:41:35Z","_id":"aa6bb842-258b-4fb6-a3d6-405f9b2e14b0","_key":"b00846c778ce","_rev":"R4bDO5qNaIcYVJNTEZsDyn","_type":"taxonomyProduct","_updatedAt":"2025-05-30T08:07:28Z","deprecated":false,"description":null,"displayName":"Krak App","editable":false,"name":"Product: Krak App","topArticles":[],"visibility":[{"_key":"b8f40c74cad0","component":"searchFilter","value":true}]},{"_createdAt":"2025-03-06T16:06:26Z","_id":"product-ConsumerWeb","_key":"9f5261776fef","_rev":"R4bDO5qNaIcYVJNTEZsDyn","_type":"taxonomyProduct","_updatedAt":"2025-05-30T08:07:28Z","deprecated":false,"description":"","displayName":"Kraken (kraken.com/c)","editable":false,"name":"Product: Consumer Web","topArticles":[],"visibility":[{"_key":"0eb60336eeeb","component":"searchFilter","value":true}]},{"_createdAt":"2025-03-06T16:06:26Z","_id":"product-ConsumerApp","_key":"0a57e1a03f30","_rev":"R4bDO5qNaIcYVJNTEZsDyn","_type":"taxonomyProduct","_updatedAt":"2025-05-30T08:07:28Z","deprecated":false,"description":"","displayName":"Kraken App","editable":false,"name":"Product: Consumer App","topArticles":[{"_key":"d6be4e502938","reference":{"_ref":"article-360049744652","_type":"page","_id":"article-360049744652","_system":{"base":{"id":"article-360049744652","rev":"8tMnvPzY4ctUNnHRoeLT5u"}},"appId":"support","content_source_locale":"en_us","enabled_locales":[],"field_page_components":[{"_key":"1b98253c5479","_type":"paragraphArticleLayout","field_article_breadcrumb_label":"Support","field_article_breadcrumbs":true,"field_children":[{"_key":"63380881f524","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Our app, simply named &quot;Kraken&quot;, offers a vibrant design and new features not available on the Kraken Pro app. It is beginner friendly and meant for easily buying and selling crypto.\u003c/p>\u003cp>With the Kraken app, you can:\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"26179a3289ea","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"fce6ba8f8428","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"0a9bc68fcb3f","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003ca href=\"/articles/360059110151\" >Create and verify a new account\u003c/a>.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"3fdf83d7f9e1","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"a6a0f9e70062","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Set up \u003ca href=\"/articles/360000911823\" >sign-in 2FA\u003c/a>.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"51eaa002dc2e","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"8acd7d80cc1b","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003ca href=\"/articles/360058727972\" >Buy, sell\u003c/a> \u003ca href=\"/articles/360058727972\" >and convert\u003c/a> cryptocurrencies.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"46b0fabf9c6b","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"bef4049341c5","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Deposit and withdraw cryptocurrencies.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"e949a5751201","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"61438725b1fb","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Make \u003ca href=\"/articles/360048212832\" >credit and debit card purchases\u003c/a>.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"fea15e7bc25f","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"c6447fae2606","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Make \u003ca href=\"/articles/8795459449492-How-do-I-fund-my-account-with-USD-using-ACH-via-Plaid-\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">ACH online banking payments\u003c/a>.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"fe078552a3dc","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"0bcef17dc719","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Find deposit information.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"5bebadc8ed5f","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"08a1f7ca92ba","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Initiate cash withdrawals.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"3bcf6344d53b","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"a51e13e380d3","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003ca href=\"/articles/360059154531#expander-control-1040612906\" >Manage approved devices\u003c/a>.\u003c/p>"}]}],"field_type":"ul"},{"_key":"539e31bbae8a","_type":"paragraphArticleHeadingBody","field_body":"","field_heading":" Frequently Asked Questions ","field_level":3},{"_key":"83794805ad45","_type":"paragraphAccordion","field_children":[{"_key":"c20c725e3a73","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"d6eaefb4a0f5","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>You can scan the following QR code on your phone or tap the links below to download:\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"a7bdd5a3a23a","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_image":{"alt":"QR","asset":{"_ref":"image-8ebc70f261a1b20f9bb53dcbb5adfa35945148f6-500x500-jpg","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/jpeg","originalFilename":"KrakenApp QR code.webp","size":61921,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":1,"height":500,"width":500},"lqip":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"_id":"image-8ebc70f261a1b20f9bb53dcbb5adfa35945148f6-500x500-jpg","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/8ebc70f261a1b20f9bb53dcbb5adfa35945148f6-500x500.jpg"}},"field_width":"auto"},{"_key":"94edf51f54cc","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTable","field_rows":[{"_key":"fe34d7d09090","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTableRow","field_cells":[{"_key":"7cc6c58b7746","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTableCell","cell_description":"Column ::  Google Play Android 8.0+ (9.0+ recommended) ","field_content":"\u003cp>\u003ca href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kraken.invest.app\" >\u003cstrong>Google Play\u003c/strong>\u003c/a> Android 8.0+ (9.0+ recommended)\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"7f3baf753cae","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTableCell","cell_description":"Column ::  Apple App Store iOS 13+ ","field_content":"\u003cp>\u003ca href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/id1481947260\" >\u003cstrong>Apple App Store\u003c/strong>\u003c/a> iOS 15+\u003c/p>"}],"row_description":"Row ::  Google Play Android 8.0+ (9.0+ recommended) "}],"table_description":"Table: Legacy Migrated Placeholder","table_expanded_table":false,"table_mobile_style":"summary"},{"_key":"209ca9c420e6","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003c/p>"}],"field_id":"nFMZ9uTl-3g2DA2tcCM4S","field_title":"Where can I download the app?"},{"_key":"83962abf6c84","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"688ead36faba","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>To see where the app is currently unavailable, see \u003ca href=\"/articles/where-is-kraken-licensed-or-regulated\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">Where is Kraken licensed or regulated?\u003c/a>\u003c/p>\u003cp>This is an app store restriction and not related to your current address registered with Kraken.\u003c/p>"}],"field_id":"ZfJmHlUhQfgnp5OhgFW-I","field_title":"Why am I not seeing the app in Google Play or Apple App stores?"},{"_key":"e64c49fbe0ec","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"53258d22dca8","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>The default currency in the app is based on your location. You can change your displayed currency by going to the &quot;Account&quot; tab, selecting &quot;Currency&quot; and then choosing a currency. We currently support USD, EUR, CAD, GBP, CHF, and AUD.\u003c/p>"}],"field_id":"D5U65eQ23cI8Os-kE2L4O","field_title":"How do I change my app currency?"},{"_key":"d3f16dc898ab","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"68bd27797cae","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>We have \u003ca href=\"/articles/360000426923\" >a comprehensive guide on 2FA methods\u003c/a> you can follow. Currently, only sign-in 2FA is fully compatible with this app.If you have Funding 2FA enabled on your account, you can place orders from current balances but it won&#x27;t be possible to place orders with a card.With Trading 2FA enabled, you can place orders from current balances but you can not add or delete cards or make card payments. With the Global Settings Lock enabled you can not add or delete cards. \u003c/p>\u003cp>\u003cstrong>To set up sign-in 2FA in the app:\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"25f3d99d6f9c","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"0de96b239fde","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"d3619ab0ee16","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Tap on the \u003cstrong>Account\u003c/strong> tab.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"90fffa8fbf58","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"8c875d669931","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Tap on to \u003cstrong>Security\u003c/strong> and scroll down to \u003cstrong>Two Factor Authentication\u003c/strong>.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"1ac028cc35ed","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"8ad81049487e","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Select either \u003ca href=\"/articles/360000444903\" >Authenticator App\u003c/a> or \u003ca href=\"/articles/360000444186\" >Passkeys.\u003c/a>\u003c/p>"}]}],"field_type":"ol"},{"_key":"c8d9030ef5e8","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>To set up 2FA with a Passkey:\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"1bc30334114f","_type":"paragraphArticleInteractiveVideo","field_video_url":"https://youtu.be/C163naN8xZw"},{"_key":"1698c7d21109","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>To complete the process, follow the on-screen instructions as they appear within the app. The process may differ depending on what device you use. \u003c/p>\u003cp>For more help, see \u003ca href=\"/articles/how-to-enable-multiple-2fa#fd6e9845b481\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">How to create Passkeys on a phone or tablet\u003c/a>. \u003c/p>\u003cp>\u003c/p>\u003cp>\u003cstrong>To set up 2FA with an Authenticator App:\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"db8ac3fb1cbd","_type":"paragraphArticleInteractiveVideo","field_video_url":"https://youtube.com/shorts/GoGxAAowsNo"},{"_key":"036999389e86","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"2913406bc909","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"ac855a52253f","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Make sure you have an Authenticator App installed.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"0a4ab022060d","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"e98e269e7ec0","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Select Authenticator App after tapping on Two Factor Authentication.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"b55465e125ad","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"2b89e53bfb55","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Your Authenticator App will open automatically - tap OK to save the key for your Kraken account.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"c2b1b8644926","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"b647f6f66e45","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>We recommend going back to the app at this point to save your secret key somewhere safe for backup, and then tap Next.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"d793a951e828","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"e8f54fab0edb","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Go back to the Authenticator App and copy the one-time passcode for your new account&#x27;s 2FA entry.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"3a229bfe5e9c","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"517e2c5324dc","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Paste or type the one-time passcode into the Kraken app.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"aaa59e7654d8","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"c6c4b61abca6","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Success! You have successfully enabled sign-in 2FA for your account.\u003c/p>"}]}],"field_type":"ol"}],"field_id":"HE_JyQz716rHAsTmOOrV8","field_title":"How do I set up two-factor authentication (2FA)?"},{"_key":"dca988c10d05","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"08968b65b881","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>In order to protect your account security, the Kraken app recommends that you provide your devices unlock credentials to access the app. This can be whichever method you use to unlock your phone such as biometrics (fingerprint, facial recognition, etc.) or a PIN. If your device does not have a PIN registered, the app will ask you to create a PIN.\u003c/p>"}],"field_id":"kyWzWpCelWrMAHMmWaTJW","field_title":"Why is the app asking for a PIN when I haven't set one up yet?"},{"_key":"422fbfc94cad","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"6e9fafe18722","_type":"paragraphArticleInteractiveVideo","field_video_url":"https://youtube.com/shorts/gFSz5kXBog8"}],"field_id":"efa898e9a100","field_title":"How to find details about a cryptocurrency "},{"_key":"9929c816ffdb","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"d97b2c4aecc5","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Your watchlist assets appear as large cards in the Home page, allowing you to quickly view the price of assets you are interested in. By default, BTC and ETH are watchlisted. You can watchlist a new asset by opening the asset page and tapping the star button in the top right corner. To un-watch an asset, simply press the star button once again.\u003c/p>\u003cp>\u003c/p>"}],"field_id":"MssE4g_lgNKUCEdyq4VQj","field_title":"How do watchlist assets work?"},{"_key":"87b0ec8c5615","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"6f41fd842c85","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>The app is currently available in:\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"eddf5d7582c6","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"5f17e24784db","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"95d47d0ab916","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Chinese\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"04d09bd26151","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"3e93999b76be","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Dutch \u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"c2fd55d2e3ff","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"59d708266c88","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp> English\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"68dc111ed304","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"6a9ed17b227b","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>French\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"b64d3c777d9b","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"a7160ffa7898","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>German\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"c45be2416b2b","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"12d26bca1ce6","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Italian \u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"afff07a327eb","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"75f54d64e15c","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Polish\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"ade13616398a","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"daa1fe8d6880","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Portuguese\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"1d59a4474547","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"d68359781aeb","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Spanish\u003c/p>"}]}],"field_type":"ul"},{"_key":"4c17aae92576","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Keep an eye on our Support Center and social channels to find out when the app will be available in additional languages.  To change the language:\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"a7550d29d4dd","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"30947f204270","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"684407eebc4b","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Navigate to the \u003cstrong>Account\u003c/strong> tab.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"04b470889f13","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"ecd530e26ff9","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Under Settings tap on \u003cstrong>Language\u003c/strong>.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"78b8df6c27d1","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"0a559fcf8c9d","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Choose your preferred language from the available options. \u003c/p>"}]}],"field_type":"ol"},{"_key":"8cadab5b00d6","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003c/p>"}],"field_id":"RtujLz6RIetS4MWnVTk6m","field_title":"How can I see the app translated in my language?"},{"_key":"2293110fcf23","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"21f1efb4f1f0","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Yes, you can convert between cryptocurrencies within the app.\u003c/p>"}],"field_id":"bXBln3udCLe3xsEv7KwZ7","field_title":"Can I convert between two cryptocurrencies?"},{"_key":"acb236bd81aa","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"6e269ad19797","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>On the final order confirmation page before making a purchase you will see a confirmation of your purchase and a full breakdown of \u003ca href=\"/articles/360060101312#h_01F4CQKMZKSJQW229HD61ZM15Q\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">fees, which will depend on the payment method being used\u003c/a>. \u003c/p>\u003cp>\u003cem>Note: While Kraken displays these fees for our clients, this is not consistent across all trading platforms. Platforms/services that do not disclose their fees typically build them into the spread, which would result in paying higher than the current market rate.\u003c/em>\u003c/p>"}],"field_id":"B1DY8JsYTBAZUUV6fTLp-","field_title":"What are the fees when buying or selling crypto instantly for cash on the app?"},{"_key":"b67ade26dca8","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"924313f866f2","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Price alerts are available on the Kraken app. To set this up, see our article on \u003ca href=\"/articles/price-alerts#fa60234bc7b5\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">Market Alerts\u003c/a>. \u003c/p>"}],"field_id":"KH1NP5Zk3M5ZRFpseMX4C","field_title":"How can I receive price alerts?"},{"_key":"5ee7b1cc9d7f","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"b3034042797c","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>You can visualize how your historical portfolio has performed over time with the line chart view. A 1 month view is selected by default. You can choose from any of the following time ranges, 1 month, 3 months, 6 months, 1 year and ALL.   Portfolio performance can be manually calculated by exporting your account history.\u003c/p>"}],"field_id":"9_382JvKTO5YqhNOGrkO3","field_title":"How can I see my portfolio performance?"}]},{"_key":"5b4936663250","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003c/p>"}],"field_last_updated_label":"Last updated:","field_title":"Kraken app: frequently asked questions","field_tldr_title":"Key takeaways"}],"field_page_meta":{"description":"Support Center for Kraken.com | Bitcoin & Cryptocurrency Exchange | Bitcoin Trading Platform","title":"Kraken app: frequently asked questions | Kraken"},"field_tags":[{"_key":"ff300f3d9409","_ref":"8acf30f1-ab2c-48b7-a789-0f46d836c3cd","_type":"taxonomyTag","_id":"8acf30f1-ab2c-48b7-a789-0f46d836c3cd","firstPublishedAt":"2026-01-20T10:38:23.492Z","lastPublishedAt":"2026-01-20T10:38:23.492Z","name":"sc-tier-1"}],"field_target_languages":["de_de","es_es","fr_fr","it_it","nl_nl","pl_pl","pt_br","ru_ru","tr_tr","uk_ua","vi_vn","zh_cn"],"lastPublishedAt":"2025-08-08T22:48:40.546Z","locale":{"_ref":"6a947fc0-ff5d-4972-a190-1bde98fa51a3","_type":"taxonomyLocales","_id":"6a947fc0-ff5d-4972-a190-1bde98fa51a3","code":"en-us","field_label":"English","name":"en-US"},"path":"/articles/360049744652-kraken-app-frequently-asked-questions","status":true,"title":"Kraken app: frequently asked questions"}},{"_key":"b5719f144ec3","reference":{"_ref":"article-7915790970516","_type":"page","_id":"article-7915790970516","_system":{"base":{"id":"article-7915790970516","rev":"nvZcks16ldBXxsacBPqp0C"}},"appId":"support","content_source_locale":"en_us","enabled_locales":[],"field_page_components":[{"_key":"a21a1c2bcc9f","_type":"paragraphArticleLayout","field_article_breadcrumb_label":"Support","field_article_breadcrumbs":true,"field_children":[{"_key":"5e5fdd126676","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Invite your friends to Kraken through our \u003ca href=\"https://www.kraken.com/referrals\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">referral program\u003c/a> and you can earn up to a $1000 bonus, when they sign up and trade with the Kraken app! This article will walk you through the referral process and answer any questions you may have.\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"4481420e60f7","_type":"paragraphAccordion","field_children":[{"_key":"1a110df73251","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"add9a961ca92","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"6f39f3550bc9","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"107967661d30","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Share your referral link: \u003c/strong>Invite your friends to Kraken by \u003ca href=\"#8c8ecc7dd5b5\">sending them your unique referral link\u003c/a> from the Kraken app.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"85c6e52c9539","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"e14ee4dd71f6","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Friend signs up: \u003c/strong>Your friend must use your referral link to create a new Kraken account via the Kraken app.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"a168231ef86b","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"2c4efce4e493","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Make a deposit: \u003c/strong>They need to deposit cash into their Kraken account.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"f248c954a51b","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"1e1fd2e8f882","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Start trading:\u003c/strong> Once they trade crypto, you both receive the referral bonus!\u003c/p>"}]}],"field_type":"ol"},{"_key":"d8420fb34c31","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cblockquote>\u003cstrong>The deposit and trading conditions required are variable. Be sure to review the specific terms applicable in your Kraken app.\u003c/strong>\u003c/blockquote>"}],"field_id":"c2f90c7cc949","field_title":"How it works"},{"_key":"342021a5cd58","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"b1c0dbefdd19","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>To be eligible to refer a friend, you must meet the following requirements:\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"033243a48475","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"1285e0ea6f1d","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"845651747623","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Location: \u003c/strong>You are located in the USA*, Puerto Rico, Australia, Brazil, Canada, Denmark, Germany, Netherlands, France, Spain, Poland, Italy, Belgium, or Ireland.\u003c/p>\u003cp>*Maine and New York are excluded\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"b2a77386b13b","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"2556ed31049d","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Account verification:\u003c/strong> You have a verified Kraken account.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"a749954c9644","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"03ee502b9ea0","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Referee: \u003c/strong>Your friend or \u003cem>Referee\u003c/em> must \u003cstrong>not\u003c/strong> have previously created a Kraken account, and they must sign up via the Kraken app to be eligible.\u003c/p>"}]}],"field_type":"ul"},{"_key":"3ae4cbc651c7","_type":"paragraphNotification","field_can_be_closed":false,"field_direction":"inline","field_has_icon":true,"field_text":"\u003cp>\u003c/p>\u003cp>Duplicate accounts and devices will be disqualified.\u003c/p>","field_title":" ","field_tone":"warning"},{"_key":"5af7c0d3e444","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cblockquote>As a reminder please use the Kraken app when referring a friend to Kraken. Your friend must sign up via the Kraken app to be eligible.\u003c/blockquote>"}],"field_id":"a629928a30d5","field_title":"Am I eligible?"},{"_key":"667f51796d6c","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"3fe0b3f14fb2","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cblockquote>Important: The friend you refer must reside in the same country as you reside, or, if you reside in an eligible European Economic Area (EEA) country, they may reside in any other eligible EEA country.\u003c/blockquote>\u003cp>\u003cstrong>To refer your friends:\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"153e6eb3cccb","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"c87516d5e7c3","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"fa6bd4729095","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Open your Kraken app.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"e58dd229d778","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"1faf92523b02","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Tap on the \u003cstrong>Gift\u003c/strong> notification (top right) then tap\u003cstrong> Invite friends\u003c/strong> to generate your referral link.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"f78bcfa5755b","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"a85554e00d56","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>You can also copy the code to share later.\u003cbr/>\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"b82897be7033","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_image":{"alt":"Home","asset":{"_ref":"image-28a0a4df6f9278792da1ac5eed0f9ab0e1afbf24-393x760-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"Home-referral-dot.png","size":81617,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":0.5171052631578947,"height":760,"width":393},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-28a0a4df6f9278792da1ac5eed0f9ab0e1afbf24-393x760-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/28a0a4df6f9278792da1ac5eed0f9ab0e1afbf24-393x760.png"}},"field_width":"auto"},{"_key":"b9de5c8a1690","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_image":{"alt":"invite","asset":{"_ref":"image-fcf5c8949b564f57e027fffb6ee5a0237e3f3afe-393x699-jpg","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/jpeg","originalFilename":"Referrer-home-empty.jpeg","size":22855,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":0.5622317596566524,"height":699,"width":393},"lqip":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"_id":"image-fcf5c8949b564f57e027fffb6ee5a0237e3f3afe-393x699-jpg","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/fcf5c8949b564f57e027fffb6ee5a0237e3f3afe-393x699.jpg"}},"field_width":"auto"}]},{"_key":"9c8487aaffb7","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"e6a60b03f7f9","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Share your link. Either send the copied link directly to your friends or, if you tapped \u003cstrong>Invite friends,\u003c/strong> share it via your chosen communication platform.\u003cbr/>\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"b2858ff970db","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"789c0c7c4989","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>That’s it! Now you can help your friend get started with the \u003ca href=\"#56fbcdf6ff63\">steps below.\u003c/a>\u003c/p>"}]}],"field_type":"ol"},{"_key":"4c398a3e879d","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003c/p>"}],"field_id":"8c8ecc7dd5b5","field_title":"How do I refer my friends to Kraken?"},{"_key":"7e87da39359e","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"7b1d71cc1a7d","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cblockquote>\u003cstrong>As a reminder please use the Kraken app when completing the steps below.\u003c/strong>\u003c/blockquote>\u003cp>If you received a referral link or code, follow these simple steps.\u003c/p>\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Using a referral link:\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"a60f6ff60109","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"afca88236441","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"46ceb53afc91","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Follow the referral link to download the Kraken app and\u003ca href=\"/articles/360059110151-Creating-and-verifying-your-account-on-the-Kraken-app\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\"> create your Kraken account.\u003c/a>\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"eb549fb015b6","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"e0360df391ec","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Once your account is activated follow \u003ca href=\"#024709fd16e4\">next steps here\u003c/a> to qualify for a bonus.\u003c/p>"}]}],"field_type":"ol"},{"_key":"bd82b2094399","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>\u003cbr/>Using a unique referral code:\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>\u003cp>Your unique referral code isn&#x27;t necessary to continue when it comes to making an account, but it is necessary to use it to enroll in the referral program\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"0ff16041d66d","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"c433efbc7281","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"73f0273b2a57","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Download the Kraken app and \u003ca href=\"/articles/360059110151-Creating-and-verifying-your-account-on-the-Kraken-app\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">create your Kraken account.\u003c/a>\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"a3dab37249c3","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_image":{"alt":"Home","asset":{"_ref":"image-0a29d98f9f25856bfd0e4cbe2a54498baf8c7d5b-393x760-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"Home.png","size":61479,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":0.5171052631578947,"height":760,"width":393},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-0a29d98f9f25856bfd0e4cbe2a54498baf8c7d5b-393x760-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/0a29d98f9f25856bfd0e4cbe2a54498baf8c7d5b-393x760.png"}},"field_width":"auto"},{"_key":"90dbbfe60542","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"1a02e37e2d9a","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"5d71e443a9d8","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>During account creation you can enter your referral code.\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"2cb51ced1408","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_image":{"alt":"Code","asset":{"_ref":"image-4a9286f0092d36e39264930d4c8aee33ba7ca171-393x494-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"code-filled2.png","size":28876,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":0.7955465587044535,"height":494,"width":393},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-4a9286f0092d36e39264930d4c8aee33ba7ca171-393x494-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/4a9286f0092d36e39264930d4c8aee33ba7ca171-393x494.png"}},"field_width":"auto"}]},{"_key":"95da8481197d","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"b72d9b2f83fc","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Once your account is \u003ca href=\"/articles/360059110151-Creating-and-verifying-your-account-on-the-Kraken-app#d0ed04ec990f\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">\u003cstrong>activated and verified \u003c/strong>\u003c/a>you can start the referral steps.\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"071771812b97","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_image":{"alt":"Next","asset":{"_ref":"image-332fd5c5624f5bab91c090be264606bece3464f5-393x501-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"sheet.png","size":75315,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":0.7844311377245509,"height":501,"width":393},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-332fd5c5624f5bab91c090be264606bece3464f5-393x501-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/332fd5c5624f5bab91c090be264606bece3464f5-393x501.png"}},"field_width":"auto"}]}],"field_type":"ol"}],"field_id":"56fbcdf6ff63","field_title":"A friend referred me, what do I need to do to earn the referral bonus?"},{"_key":"ae10f6c8ba03","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"416ad3c84e77","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>The deposit and trading conditions required are variable. Be sure to review the specific terms applicable in your Kraken app.\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"169f31224299","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"ba6bd886e960","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"0efbb4cdf896","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003ca href=\"/articles/depositing-and-withdrawing-funds-from-the-kraken-app-refresh#P6Rp5ZczbPW3KakWhy6zQ\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">Deposit fiat (cash)\u003c/a> to your new Kraken account. The amount required will be shown in your app.\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"bec2f2d81f58","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"2e365c188d9b","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Trade crypto: Make one trade or multiple trades to reach the total required amount outlined in your Kraken app. \u003cbr/>\u003c/p>"}]}],"field_type":"ul"},{"_key":"e36c5e689106","_type":"paragraphArticleImage","field_image":{"alt":"Steps","asset":{"_ref":"image-6edff90ba55279c743808396b2ef66cef4b292eb-393x710-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"referral-home-2.png","size":39848,"metadata":{"dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":0.5535211267605634,"height":710,"width":393},"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,"},"_id":"image-6edff90ba55279c743808396b2ef66cef4b292eb-393x710-png","sanityUrl":"https://assets-cms.kraken.com/images/51n36hrp/facade/6edff90ba55279c743808396b2ef66cef4b292eb-393x710.png"}},"field_width":"auto"},{"_key":"a60e85c21026","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>You can use most deposit options available on the Kraken app, excluding debit/ credit card deposits.\u003c/p>"}],"field_id":"024709fd16e4","field_title":"To qualify for the referral bonus"},{"_key":"533c23c8b58f","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"7b107e01e695","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>You can trade using the following Kraken platforms, but please ensure that you signup using the Kraken mobile app. \u003c/p>"},{"_key":"13c6568142ab","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyList","field_list_items":[{"_key":"64e6eb7c9f07","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"f49135b40f76","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Trade in the Kraken app by \u003ca data-testid=\"external-link\" href=\"/articles/360058727972-Buying-selling-and-converting-cryptocurrency-with-the-Kraken-app#e95a90c58b77\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"blank\">Converting cash to crypto\u003c/a>, or using a \u003ca data-testid=\"external-link\" href=\"/articles/10371946346132-Custom-orders-on-the-Kraken-app-\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"blank\">Custom order \u003c/a>or \u003ca data-testid=\"external-link\" href=\"/articles/6906240918804-Recurring-buys-on-the-Kraken-app\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"blank\">Recurring order.\u003c/a>&nbsp;\u003cbr />\n\u003cbr />\n\u003cstrong>Please note: Bundles and stablecoins are not eligible trading methods.\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>\n"}]},{"_key":"8367f797d3a8","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"cc7dbe0f383f","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Trade via \u003ca href=\"/articles/360051144472-Buying-Crypto-on-Kraken#54wKspvbDKjjTMr88LxR6\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">Kraken web by using the convert feature.\u003c/a>\u003c/p>"}]},{"_key":"f04e55a0f9bd","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyListItem","field_children":[{"_key":"baa4eee10425","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Trade via \u003ca href=\"/articles/kraken-pro-trading-interface-guide\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">Kraken Pro\u003c/a> or \u003ca href=\"/articles/360056804571-How-to-place-orders-with-the-Kraken-Pro-app\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">Kraken pro app.\u003c/a>\u003c/p>"}]}],"field_type":"ul"},{"_key":"b025a86f8dd8","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>\u003c/p>"}],"field_id":"0e26b4a9f8fc","field_title":"How do I trade?"},{"_key":"675aff148c38","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"059eb7b71721","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Qualifying trades will depend on the referral plan you signed up for.\u003c/p>\n"}],"field_id":"ad9b38a7d919","field_title":"Can I trade using Kraken Pro? (app or web)"},{"_key":"373f377714d2","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"0616977888d4","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Yes, after you create your new Kraken account, you will have \u003cstrong>30 days\u003c/strong> to perform the required actions. A countdown will be shown in your app.\u003c/p>"}],"field_id":"face395a8b86","field_title":"Is there a deadline for the Referee to perform the required actions?"},{"_key":"9ee4b7a7365a","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"c9f91159ca3c","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>The bonus payout is a fixed amount of $20 in your default currency. This could be €20 worth of BTC, CA$20 of BTC, $20 USDG).\u003c/p>"}],"field_id":"33e15e478bda","field_title":"How much is the referral bonus?"},{"_key":"fa2bde13b17f","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"835ebe77d7a7","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>Within 14 days of completing \u003ca target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://www.kraken.com/legal/referrals\">term conditions.\u003c/a>\u003c/p>\u003cp>The bonus amount and form (digital assets or legal tender) are determined by Kraken and specified in the applicable Referral Bonus offer. \u003ca target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://www.kraken.com/referrals\">Referral Bonuses are subject to program limits, eligibility rules,\u003c/a> and Kraken’s discretion, and are not guaranteed.\u003c/p>"}],"field_id":"4929727854e4","field_title":"When will I receive my referral bonus?"},{"_key":"38a39339f3a6","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"2569cf73a6ab","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp>You can track the status of your own progress in your Referrals dashboard.\u003c/p>\u003cp>To find it:\u003c/p>\u003cul>\u003cli>\u003cp>Tap the \u003cstrong>gift icon\u003c/strong> or go to \u003cstrong>More → Offers\u003c/strong> in the Kraken app\u003c/p>\u003c/li>\u003cli>\u003cp>Select \u003cstrong>Referrals\u003c/strong> to view your invite link, rewards, and referral status\u003c/p>\u003c/li>\u003c/ul>\u003cp>\u003c/p>\u003cp>You can also access it directly here: \u003ca target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://www.kraken.com/c/referrals\">https://www.kraken.com/c/referrals\u003c/a>\u003c/p>"}],"field_is_expanded":false,"field_title":"Where can i track my referrals?"}]},{"_key":"585fb81c214d","_type":"paragraphNotification","field_can_be_closed":false,"field_closed_state_is_persistent":true,"field_direction":"stacked","field_has_icon":true,"field_text":"\u003cp>\u003ca href=\"https://www.kraken.com/legal/referrals\">Terms and conditions.\u003c/a>\u003c/p>\n","field_tone":"primary"}],"field_last_updated_label":"Last updated:","field_title":"Kraken referral program","field_tldr_title":"Key takeaways"}],"field_page_meta":{"description":"Support Center for Kraken.com | Bitcoin & Cryptocurrency Exchange | Bitcoin Trading Platform","title":"Kraken app referral program | Kraken"},"field_tags":[{"_key":"1ac103ded8ca","_ref":"8acf30f1-ab2c-48b7-a789-0f46d836c3cd","_type":"taxonomyTag","_id":"8acf30f1-ab2c-48b7-a789-0f46d836c3cd","firstPublishedAt":"2026-01-20T10:38:23.492Z","lastPublishedAt":"2026-01-20T10:38:23.492Z","name":"sc-tier-1"}],"field_target_languages":["de_de","es_es","fr_fr","it_it","nl_nl","pl_pl","pt_br","ru_ru","tr_tr","uk_ua","vi_vn","zh_cn"],"is_article":true,"lastPublishedAt":"2026-06-22T19:36:07.885Z","locale":{"_ref":"6a947fc0-ff5d-4972-a190-1bde98fa51a3","_type":"taxonomyLocales","_id":"6a947fc0-ff5d-4972-a190-1bde98fa51a3","code":"en-us","field_label":"English","name":"en-US"},"path":"/articles/kraken-app-referral-program","status":true,"title":"Kraken app referral program"}},{"_key":"9ada333c0144","reference":{"_ref":"article-360000381846","_type":"page","_id":"article-360000381846","_system":{"base":{"id":"article-360000381846","rev":"DA8Qswxek4eqHiQjGQFp9W"}},"appId":"support","content_source_locale":"en_us","enabled_locales":[],"field_page_components":[{"_key":"59749a265c84","_type":"paragraphArticleLayout","field_article_breadcrumb_label":"Support","field_article_breadcrumbs":true,"field_children":[{"_key":"9ae6d4f19311","_type":"paragraphNotification","field_alternative_icon":"InfoCircle","field_can_be_closed":false,"field_direction":"inline","field_has_icon":true,"field_text":"\u003cp>\u003cp>For security, certain transactions such as \u003ca href=\"/articles/8795459449492\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">ACH,\u003c/a> \u003ca href=\"/articles/fund-your-kraken-account-with-paypal\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">Paypal\u003c/a>, \u003ca href=\"/articles/360048212832\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">debit or credit card purchases\u003c/a> or\u003ca href=\"/articles/4405883992724-Digital-wallet-purchases\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\"> digital wallet purchases\u003c/a> will trigger a temporary (72 hour) withdrawal hold. Cash deposits via \u003ca href=\"/articles/8795459449492-How-do-I-fund-my-account-with-USD-using-ACH-via-Plaid-\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">ACH Plaid\u003c/a> are held from withdrawal for 7 days. \u003cstrong>This applies to all crypto and fiat withdrawals.\u003c/strong> Debit/credit card purchases in USD may always be subject to the 72-hour hold, not just the first transaction.\u003c/p>\u003c/p>","field_title":"Withdrawal hold","field_tone":"primary"},{"_key":"9ddbe45bc783","_type":"paragraphArticleHeadingBody","field_body":"\u003cp>To \u003ca href=\"/articles/360051144472-Buying-Crypto-on-Kraken\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">buy or trade crypto on Kraken,\u003c/a> first deposit funds using a supported currency below. Choose your local currency to see available deposit options. The most common method is bank transfer.\u003c/p>","field_heading":" How can I deposit funds into my Kraken account? ","field_heading_html_id":"e75f749b5cdf","field_level":1},{"_key":"c71cb3ef12cd","_type":"paragraphArticleHeadingBody","field_body":"","field_heading":" Supported currencies ","field_heading_html_id":"22de9702d70f","field_level":1},{"_key":"e686c1fbe750","_type":"paragraphAccordion","field_children":[{"_key":"8d5b7d0f0b57","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"e1ed5d909cf2","_type":"paragraphNotification","field_can_be_closed":false,"field_direction":"inline","field_has_icon":true,"field_text":"\u003cp>\u003cp> If required and shown in the deposit instructions, make sure your deposit includes a \u003ca href=\"/articles/360000381026-Why-is-the-deposit-reference-important-\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">reference\u003c/a> to your Kraken \u003ca href=\"/articles/360028555092-How-to-find-your-account-number-Public-Account-ID-\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\">Public account ID\u003c/a> which starts with AA and is 16 characters long. \u003c/p>\u003c/p>","field_title":"Prevent deposit delays","field_tone":"warning"},{"_key":"033667e5e09d","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTable","field_rows":[{"_key":"4521540b94c3","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTableRow","field_cells":[{"_key":"e780dc52b936","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTableCell","cell_description":"Column ::  Availability ","field_content":"\u003cp>Availability\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"abac319363c8","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTableCell","cell_description":"Column ::  Deposit method ","field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>\u003cstrong>Deposit method\u003c/strong>\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"2ad44fdeb525","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTableCell","cell_description":"Column ::  Deposit minimum ","field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>\u003cstrong>Deposit minimum\u003c/strong>\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"94249d97bbb6","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTableCell","cell_description":"Column ::  Deposit fee ","field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>\u003cstrong>Deposit fee\u003c/strong>\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"200216d8b7ec","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTableCell","cell_description":"Column ::  Processing time ","field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>\u003cstrong>Processing time\u003c/strong>\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"d851c45ccc6a","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTableCell","cell_description":"Column ::  Withdrawal Hold ","field_content":"\u003cp> Withdrawal Hold \u003c/p>"}],"row_description":"Row ::  Availability "},{"_key":"e478db946711","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTableRow","field_cells":[{"_key":"352064abab9a","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTableCell","cell_description":"Column ::  Availability ","field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>USA only\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"a8feafdf0d83","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTableCell","cell_description":"Column ::  Deposit method ","field_content":"\u003cp>\u003ca href=\"https://support.kraken.com/hc/en-us/articles/8795459449492-How-do-I-fund-my-account-with-USD-using-ACH-via-Plaid-\">ACH (Plaid)\u003c/a>\u003cstrong>****\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>\n"},{"_key":"81094ce91957","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTableCell","cell_description":"Column ::  Deposit minimum ","field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>1 USD\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"10d76e31ce81","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTableCell","cell_description":"Column ::  Deposit fee ","field_content":"\u003cp>\u003cstrong>Free\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>"},{"_key":"a73f38e0a93c"